NK083('u)001:1: // gsang sngags lam rim 'grel pa rin chen phreng ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so //

NK083('u)001:7: nyams len lam rim rin chen sgron ma yi //
NK083('u)001:8: bshad 'grel rin chen phreng ba bri bar bya //
NK083('u)001:13: dang po klad don la gnyis te /
NK083('u)001:16: dang po phyag 'tshal la gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:20: dang po bsdus don la bzhi ste /
NK083('u)001:36: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'o //
NK083('u)001:37: gnyis pa dgos don la lnga /
NK083('u)001:42: des thugs dgongs rdzogs pa'i dgos pa'o //
NK083('u)001:44: gnyis bcom gnyis ldan gnyis 'das gnyis dpal mchog /bya ba ni /
NK083('u)001:46: yul dang yul can gzung ba dang 'dzin pa gnyis bcoma /
NK083('u)001:47: ldan pa gzung 'dzin gnyis med rig pa ye shes kyi dona gnyis dang ldan /
NK083('u)001:49: yod med gnyis kyi mtha' las 'adsa /
NK083('u)001:50: gnyis med kyi don rang chas su yod pa gnas pa gzhi'i dapala /
NK083('u)001:51: de ji bzhin shes pa rtogs pa mchoga gi dpal gnyis dang ldana /
NK083('u)001:52: ma lus 'dus shing yang dag zol med pa //
NK083('u)001:54: ma lusa pas na kun zhes bya ste /
NK083('u)001:55: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa lhag ma med par 'dus pas na 'dus zhes bya ste /
NK083('u)001:56: dus gsum sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa kun tu bzang po'i thugs su 'dus /
NK083('u)001:57: spyod yul mdzad pa yongas su dag pas na bzang po zhes bya ste /
NK083('u)001:58: rig pa gnyis med la gnyis 'dzin 'khrul pa'i zol med pa'o //
NK083('u)001:59: sangs rgyas bde gshegs drug pa kun tu bzang //
NK083('u)001:63: gnyis med ye shes ngo bo rgyas //
NK083('u)001:64: dgongs pa nar son pas na bde gshegsa /
NK083('u)001:65: sku lnga dbyer med pas na drug pa /
NK083('u)001:66: dgongs pa ma lus pas na kun /
NK083('u)001:68: skyod yul yongs su dag pas na bzang po'o //
NK083('u)001:69: gus gdung dad pa'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK083('u)001:73: sems dad pa'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK083('u)001:74: gnyis pa rtsom par dam bca' ba la bzhi ste /
NK083('u)001:84: bdag nyid rnal 'byor o rgyan pad 'byung gis //
NK083('u)001:86: yang dag pa'i don rtogs pa la goms pas na bdag nyid /
NK083('u)001:87: rnal ma'i don la rig pa ye shes kyi dgongs pa 'byor bas na rnal 'byor /
NK083('u)001:88: yul o rgyan du me tog pad+ma la bardzusa nas byon pas na o rgyan pada 'byung /
NK083('u)001:91: de ni sku che ba'i yon tan dang ldan zhing
NK083('u)001:92: man ngag rtsom pa'i tshad du gyur pa yin no
NK083('u)001:95: rdo rje theg pa'i tshe gcig thob byed lam //
NK083('u)001:97: rang gzhan gyi lus ngag yid gsum dang /
NK083('u)001:98: he ru ka'i sku gsung thugs dbyer mi phyed pas na rdo rje /
NK083('u)001:99: de ni y+aa na zhes pa la drangs nas theg pa ste /
NK083('u)001:100: yang dag sangs rgyas kyi sar 'degs pa'o //
NK083('u)001:101: ma na tra zhes pa la drangs na sngags te /
NK083('u)001:102: shes skyob ci nus pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK083('u)001:103: badz+ra la drangs pas rdo rje 'jig bral med pa'o //
NK083('u)001:107: rdo rje sngags kyi theg pa zhes gsungs te /
NK083('u)001:108: phyi mtshan nyid las khyad par 'phags so //
NK083('u)001:109: de yang mtshan nyid pa sangs rgya ba la mi tshe dang bskal pa mang po bgrang dgos la /
NK083('u)001:110: 'dir tshe gciga lus gcig kho nar sangs rgya ba'o //
NK083('u)001:113: phyi rabs rnal 'byor las ldan don ched du //
NK083('u)001:115: gong ma'i rjes su 'jug pas na phyi rabsa /
NK083('u)001:116: dkar po'i las 'brel yod pas na rnal 'byor /
NK083('u)001:117: gsang sngags kyi skal pa yod pas na las ldan te /
NK083('u)001:118: de dag gi don du mdzad pa'o //
NK083('u)001:121: nyams len lam rim rin chen sgron ma bri //
NK083('u)001:123: dor bya la log /blang bya la 'jug pas na nyamsa len /
NK083('u)001:124: de nyid la brten nas yang dag sangs rgyas kyi sar phyin cing bgrod par byed pas na las /
NK083('u)001:125: de'i thabs rim par ston pas na rim /
NK083('u)001:126: mchog dang thun mong gi yon tan thams cad 'byung ba na rat+na /
NK083('u)001:127: ma rig pa'i mun pa sel bar byed pas na sgron ma zhes bya'o //
NK083('u)001:128: gnyis pa gzhung gi don la gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:132: dang po gzhi la gnyis te /
NK083('u)001:135: dang po gnas lugs ngos bzung ba ni /
NK083('u)001:136: gnyis med lhun grub ka dag ye sangs rgyas //
NK083('u)001:139: dang po gnyis med du gnas pa'i gnas lugs so //
NK083('u)001:141: cir yang snang la gang du yang nges pa med pas /
NK083('u)001:142: ngo bo snang stong gnyis meda /
NK083('u)001:143: sems nyid gdod ma nas ma skyes la /
NK083('u)001:144: ma skyes pa nyid cir yang ma 'gags pas /
NK083('u)001:146: snang tshad rang gi sems yin la /
NK083('u)001:147: sems pas ma gtogs pa'i chos gzhan med pas /
NK083('u)001:148: snang ba rang snang gnyis med /
NK083('u)001:149: rang snang gnyis med kyi sems de sngar med gsar du byung ba ma yin te /
NK083('u)001:151: gnas lugs rang gzhan gnyis med /
NK083('u)001:152: de ltar gnyis med ma yin pa'i chos gzhan med pas /
NK083('u)001:154: mdor na chos nyid stong pa las /
NK083('u)001:155: chos can 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad snang rung mi 'gags pa 'char bas /
NK083('u)001:156: gnyis meda ma tha' las grol ba'o //
NK083('u)001:157: de ltar gnyis med du ngo sprod pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK083('u)001:158: gzhan sel gyis gnyis chos tha dad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa grol ba /
NK083('u)001:159: don gnyis gnyis med rtogs pa /
NK083('u)001:160: ngo bo gnyis bsdus kyi chos thams cad gnyis med thig le nyag gcig tu gnas pa'o //
NK083('u)001:161: gnyis pa lhun grub tu gnas pa'i gnas lugs la yang lnga las /
NK083('u)001:162: chos thams cad kyi gshis cir yang ma grub pa ni /
NK083('u)001:164: chos thams cad kyi rtsal cir yang ma 'gags pa ni /
NK083('u)001:166: chos thams cad kyi ngo bo cir yang mi rtog pa ni /
NK083('u)001:168: de gzhan gyis byas pa ma yin te /
NK083('u)001:169: gdod ma nas de ltar grub pa ni /
NK083('u)001:171: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la lhun grub ma yin pa'i chos gzhan med pas /
NK083('u)001:173: mdor na chos nyid stong pa la /
NK083('u)001:174: chos can 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad 'byung rung du grub la /
NK083('u)001:175: bden pa rang rgyud du mi gnas pas /
NK083('u)001:176: lhun grub mtha' dang bral ba'o //
NK083('u)001:177: de ltar lhun grub tu ngo sprad pas //
NK083('u)001:178: gzhan sel gzhan nas rtsol ba'i zhen pa grol ba'o //
NK083('u)001:179: don gnyer btsal zhing bsgrub mi dgos par /
NK083('u)001:180: rtogs pa'i ngo bo snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang gi sems su lhun grub pa'o //
NK083('u)001:181: gsum pa gzhi rnam dag tu gnas pa'i gnas lugs la yang lnga las /
NK083('u)001:182: rang bzhin stong pa nyid la dngos po'i chos gansa daga pa ni /
NK083('u)001:184: stong pa'i rtsal 'gags med du rang snang ba la
NK083('u)001:185: rang rgyud kyi bden pa ka nas dag pa ni
NK083('u)001:186: / ye shes rnam dag /ngo bo snang stong gnyis
NK083('u)001:187: med la tha dad kyi chos gnas dag pa ni
NK083('u)001:189: de glo bur du byas pa ma yin te gdod nas yod pa ni /
NK083('u)001:190: rang bzhin rnam dag /ka daga ma yin pa'i chos gzhan med pa ni /
NK083('u)001:192: mdor na chos nyid stong pa la chos can 'khor
NK083('u)001:193: 'das kyi chos thams cad snang rung du ma spangs
NK083('u)001:194: la / rang bzhin rnam par dang pas /
NK083('u)001:196: de ltar rnam dag tu ngo sprod pas /
NK083('u)001:197: gzhan sel 'khrul ba rang rgyud par 'dzin pa'i zhen pa grol ba /
NK083('u)001:198: don gnyer rnam dag rtogs ba /
NK083('u)001:199: ngo bo chos nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'o //
NK083('u)001:200: bzhi pa ye nas sangs rgyas su gnas pa'i gnas lugs ni /
NK083('u)001:201: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems te /
NK083('u)001:203: gnyis med ye shes rgyas pas sangs rgyas so //
NK083('u)001:204: de yang 'khrul pa yod pa gcig med par sangs nas /
NK083('u)001:205: gnyis med med pa gcig yod par rgyas pa ni ma yin te /
NK083('u)001:206: gshis la 'khrul pa ma grub cing //
NK083('u)001:207: ngo bo gnyis med ye shes su rgyas pas ye nas sangsa rgyas pa yin te /
NK083('u)001:208: rang bzhin stong pa chos sku /
NK083('u)001:209: rang mdangs gsal ba longs sku /
NK083('u)001:210: gsal stong gnyis med sprul sku /
NK083('u)001:216: dbyer med de mkhyen pa'i ye shes so //
NK083('u)001:219: ngo bo gnyis med du yod pa /
NK083('u)001:221: de ltar ye nas sangs rgyas ma yin na /
NK083('u)001:222: bsgoms kyang sangs rgyas mi 'byung ste /
NK083('u)001:223: sa le sbram ye nas gser ma yin na /
NK083('u)001:224: byas kyang gser du mi 'gro ba bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:225: de ltar ye nas sangs rgyas su bstan pas /
NK083('u)001:226: gzhan sel gzhi la grub par 'dod pa'i zhen pa grol ba /
NK083('u)001:227: don gnyis ye nas sangs rgyas su rtogs pa /
NK083('u)001:228: ngo bo rang rig sku dang ye shes su rtogs pa'o //
NK083('u)001:230: snying po ma rig las nyon log sdug bsngal /
NK083('u)001:234: sems nyid bde gshegs snying po yod med kyi mtha' dang bral ba'o //
NK083('u)001:235: de nyid rang ngo ma shes pa la /
NK083('u)001:236: yod med 'dra mi 'drar bzung nas 'khrul lo //
NK083('u)001:240: dang po lhan cig skyes pa ni /
NK083('u)001:241: rig par ngo ma shes pa'o //
NK083('u)001:243: gang gis ngo ma shes na /
NK083('u)001:247: rgyu mtshan ston mkhan med nas /
NK083('u)001:248: tshul mun khang gi gzugs ltar /
NK083('u)001:249: dpe tho la thor ma shes pa bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:250: gnyis pa kun tu btags pa ni /
NK083('u)001:251: med pa la yod par btags pa'o //
NK083('u)001:252: de yang gang gis btags na /
NK083('u)001:258: dpe tho la mir btags pa bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:260: las gsum dang nyon mongs lnga'o //
NK083('u)001:261: de yang dge ba'i las kyis 'dod khams kyi lha mi la sogs pa mtho ris su skye ba /
NK083('u)001:262: ma g.yo bas tshangs ris su skye zhing /
NK083('u)001:263: mi dge bas ngan song du skye'o //
NK083('u)001:267: gti mug gis dud 'gro /phrag dog gis lha min /
NK083('u)001:268: nga rgyal gyis lha dang mi ru skye'o //
NK083('u)001:269: de yang las gsum dang ldan pa'i nus pa'o //
NK083('u)001:270: bzhi pa byed pa po ni /
NK083('u)001:271: log rtog gi skad cig ma yin te /
NK083('u)001:272: de'i rgyun sbrel ba las 'khor ba'i chos 'byung bas /
NK083('u)001:273: ma dag pa'i gzhan dbang ngo //
NK083('u)001:274: de yang stong pa las spros pa byung /
NK083('u)001:275: des rig pa la bdag tu bzung /
NK083('u)001:276: bdag la ltos nas gzhan byung ste /
NK083('u)001:277: gzhan gyi cha las chags sdang rmongs gsum skyes //
NK083('u)001:279: las rnams smin du myong ste /
NK083('u)001:280: log rtog gi skad cig ma rgyun dang bcas pas /
NK083('u)001:282: yod par dmigs pa la brten nas /
NK083('u)001:283: rtag pa don ltar du chags /
NK083('u)001:284: chags pa la zhen te 'khrul pa ru brtas nas 'khor ba'i chos grub bo //
NK083('u)001:286: rigs drug gi lus blangs nas /
NK083('u)001:287: gnas so so ru dug lnga sna tshogs la spyod pa'o //
NK083('u)001:289: spyi tshan du thog mtha' gnyis ka med la /
NK083('u)001:290: sgos tshan du tha ma yod pa'o //
NK083('u)001:291: de ltar 'khrul lugs bstan pa'i dgos pa gnyis te /
NK083('u)001:292: gzhan sel gyi dgos pa ni /
NK083('u)001:293: gzhi la 'khrul pa rang rgyud la grub par 'dod pa'i zhen pa grol ba'o //
NK083('u)001:294: don gnyer ba'i dgos pa ni /
NK083('u)001:295: gzhi pa 'khrul ba ma grub cing /
NK083('u)001:296: rang bzhin rnam dag rtogs pa'o //
NK083('u)001:297: de yang 'khrul ba sgro btags glo bur par 'dug
NK083('u)001:298: pas de'i rang bzhin shes na 'khrul pa rang sar
NK083('u)001:299: grol te / tho ru shes pa na med 'dzin
NK083('u)001:300: gyi 'khrul pa rang sangs su grol ba bzhin no
NK083('u)001:301: grol te / // gnyis pa lam la gsum /
NK083('u)001:306: phun sum tshogs pa lngas bsgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba /
NK083('u)001:307: srung ba'i 'khor lo'i rim pa bstan pa /
NK083('u)001:308: gnad lnga'i sgo nas lam la 'jug pa'o //
NK083('u)001:310: phun sum tshogs lngas bsgrub gzhi gzung ba ni /
NK083('u)001:317: dang po gnas gang du na /
NK083('u)001:318: brag nags dur khrod phug sogs skyon yon brtsi //
NK083('u)001:320: brag phug ma mo dang srin po'i gnas yin /
NK083('u)001:323: nags khrod klu dang gnod sbyin gyi gnas yin /
NK083('u)001:326: dur khrod gshin rje dang sha za dang /
NK083('u)001:330: sa phug the'u brang ma mo dang dam sri'i gnas yin /
NK083('u)001:332: ma mo bsgrub pa la dga' /
NK083('u)001:333: shing rkang gcig gi lha rten yod pa mu stegs kyi gnas yin /
NK083('u)001:334: dbang phyug chen po bsgrub pa la dga' /
NK083('u)001:335: de'i sogs khongs su gnas mtha' dag shes par bya'o //
NK083('u)001:336: skyon yon brtsi zhes pa la gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:337: mtshan nyid mi ldan pa'i skyon /
NK083('u)001:341: shar ri mtho na tshe la gnod /
NK083('u)001:342: nub har bor song na bkra mi shis /
NK083('u)001:343: ri sna mdung tshugs su zugs na bar chad 'ong /
NK083('u)001:344: tsha grang ma mnyam na nad 'jug /gdon gdug pa can yod na bar chad 'ong /
NK083('u)001:345: rgyu srang zugs na mi'i 'tshe ba yong /
NK083('u)001:347: steng na brag lhung du cha ba dang /
NK083('u)001:348: ngus pa'i mchi nges 'dra ba dang /
NK083('u)001:349: sder sran gyis brad pa 'dra ba /
NK083('u)001:351: sgo la grog mdo zugs pa /
NK083('u)001:352: sgo na mi langs pa lta bu byung ba rnams ni /
NK083('u)001:353: sa dgra yin pas skyon can no //
NK083('u)001:355: brag skyil mo krung byas pa 'dra na ting nge 'dzin skye /
NK083('u)001:356: pad+ma kha bye ba 'dra na rtogs pa skye /
NK083('u)001:357: sa dang gnam gru gsum du yod na 'grub thag nye /
NK083('u)001:358: rgyab ri mtho na bag dro /
NK083('u)001:359: byang ri mtho na bkra shis /
NK083('u)001:361: sa dgra gang yang mi 'dug na bkra shis te /
NK083('u)001:363: gsum pa ldan tshul ngos bzung ba ni /
NK083('u)001:364: sa pad+ma 'dab brgyad du yod pa /
NK083('u)001:365: gnam 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad du yod pa /
NK083('u)001:368: g.yas dar dkar gyi yol ba 'dra ba /
NK083('u)001:370: mda' phyag rgya bsnol ba 'dra ba /
NK083('u)001:371: ri thams cad snum zhing khengs pa /
NK083('u)001:377: chu bo dbang gi phyogs nas 'bab pa /
NK083('u)001:380: gsal cha che zhing so thub pa /
NK083('u)001:381: tsha grang snyoms shing gzhi bdag 'jam pa /
NK083('u)001:382: thag nye ring ran cing sa btsan pa /
NK083('u)001:383: bkra shis shing grub thob kyi zhabs kyis bcags pa gcig btsal lo //
NK083('u)001:386: pad+ma'i 'dab ma 'dra na lte ba la /
NK083('u)001:387: skyil krung 'dra na bsnol mtshams su /
NK083('u)001:390: phag gam glang po 'dra na mig tshil /
NK083('u)001:399: mdor na sa'i snying non pa /
NK083('u)001:400: sa ma bo zhing gzhung 'dril ba la gdab pa'o //
NK083('u)001:404: mi'i sug gsham la mi gdab pa'o //
NK083('u)001:405: sa dgra bsrung ba'i rten 'brel ni /
NK083('u)001:407: kha dog sngon po'i sa dgra yod na me'i ri mo bya /
NK083('u)001:408: grog mdo ri hrul chad pa la chu'i ri mo bya /
NK083('u)001:409: sder sen gyis brad pa'am shi lpags 'dra na bkra shis rdzas brgyad bri /
NK083('u)001:410: steng nas lhung la khad pa la mchod rten brtsigs /
NK083('u)001:411: mtshan ma bzed pa 'dra na pho rtags gzugs /
NK083('u)001:412: brag sbra tsam sgo'i thad kar na 'dug na /
NK083('u)001:413: sa dgra che bas rten 'brel mang du bya'o //
NK083('u)001:415: sems can gyi gzugs 'dra ba 'dug na /
NK083('u)001:416: de'i gnyen por gang 'gro ba'i gzugs bya'o //
NK083('u)001:418: shar du mchod rten mi brtsig go //
NK083('u)001:425: sne thung gdong thug rnams sa dgra yin pas //
NK083('u)001:426: thad kar bkra shis kyi mtshan ma dang snying po bri /
NK083('u)001:428: lho gshin rje ru sgo'i kha mi bstan /
NK083('u)001:429: lho nub srin po'i steng du mal mi bca' /
NK083('u)001:430: nub byang rlung lha'i steng du g.yos mi bya //
NK083('u)001:431: shar lho me lhar thab gzugs /
NK083('u)001:432: byang shar dbang ldan mal baca'o //
NK083('u)001:434: ri la mgo bo mthur bstan /
NK083('u)001:436: gdung gis mal gyi sked pa bcad pa /
NK083('u)001:442: lhwam zon sngas 'jug /de rnams mal gyi sa dgra yin pas mi bya'o //
NK083('u)001:443: des na sa gnad 'dom gang la /
NK083('u)001:444: dge sbyor 'phel dang mi 'phel gyi gnad yod do //
NK083('u)001:445: phyi nang snod bcud nang sems gcig gi ngo bo yin pa'i phyir /
NK083('u)001:446: rten phyi rol gyi skyon yon gang yin pa de /
NK083('u)001:447: brten pa nang sems can gyi rgyud la yod pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:449: tshes skar gza' bzang yar ngo'i snga gong 'jug /ces pas /
NK083('u)001:453: nya la sogs pa bzang ba /
NK083('u)001:457: bre la sogs pa bzang ba /
NK083('u)001:458: gza' phur bu la sogs pa dar ba'i tshe /
NK083('u)001:459: de nas zla ba yar ngo /
NK083('u)001:461: tshes dang skar ma gza' thams cad /
NK083('u)001:462: rgyud lung man ngag kun dang bstun pa'i bzang po
NK083('u)001:463: la zhugs pas don thams cad 'grub pa yin te
NK083('u)001:465: skar ma mgo lag rgyal sogs bzang po gsum gces so //
NK083('u)001:467: dad gus dbang dam shes rab gding dang ldan //
NK083('u)001:469: dad pa chen pos dkar ba'i chos la 'jug nus pa /
NK083('u)001:470: mos gus chen pos bla ma sangs rgyas su mthong ba /
NK083('u)001:471: dbang bzhi thob pas man ngag gi snod du rung ba /
NK083('u)001:472: dam tshig che bas bsgrub pa'i gzhi thengs pa /
NK083('u)001:473: shes rab che bas nges pa'i don go nus pa /
NK083('u)001:474: lta ba'i gdeng dang ldan pas nyams nga dang khu 'phrig med pa /
NK083('u)001:477: dad pa med na 'khor ba la blo mi ldog
NK083('u)001:478: /mos gus med na byin rlabs mi 'jug /dbang ma
NK083('u)001:479: thob na man ngag gi snod du mi rung /
NK083('u)001:480: dam tshig nyams na sgrub pa'i gzhi rten med /
NK083('u)001:481: shes rab med na nges pa'i don mi go //
NK083('u)001:482: lta ba'i gding dang mi ldan na bar chad 'byung bas de ltar snod du mi rung ste /
NK083('u)001:483: mtshan nyid ldan par man ngag sbyin //
NK083('u)001:484: de las gzhan la bstan mi bya //
NK083('u)001:487: zas sman mchod bskang sgrub pa'i rdzas rnams bsags //
NK083('u)001:490: 'tsho ba zas kyi yo byad bldab tu bshams te /
NK083('u)001:491: ma grub na spogs la sgrub dgos pa'o //
NK083('u)001:492: nad zlog sman gyi yo byad sman dang yi ge ru gshoms te /
NK083('u)001:493: nad byung na 'byung ba cha mnyam dgos pa'o //
NK083('u)001:495: lta ba dang dmigs pa rten 'brel gyi sgo nas kyang bcos so //
NK083('u)001:500: mdangs dang ldan pa gshams te /
NK083('u)001:501: bde gshegs thams cad dges pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:506: ro dang ldan pa bshams te /
NK083('u)001:507: dam can thugs dam bskang ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:510: lha so so'i rjes su mthun cing /
NK083('u)001:511: kha dog dri ro dang ldan pa bshams pas //
NK083('u)001:512: byin rlabs sprin bzhin 'ong ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:513: mchod pa'i rdzas kyis bde gshegs mnyes //
NK083('u)001:514: skong ba'i rdzas kyis dam can skong //
NK083('u)001:515: sgrub rdzas tshogs pas byin rlabs 'byung //
NK083('u)001:517: lnga pa sgrub pa'i thabs ni /
NK083('u)001:518: ma dred rtse gcig dka' thub mthar 'don no //
NK083('u)001:520: blo mi dred pas shes pa rtse gcig tu dril te dka' thub kyi sa rdo btsugs nas /
NK083('u)001:521: snying rus chen pos sgrub pa mtha' ru 'don no //
NK083('u)001:528: rnam rtog la sogs pa'i phyogs su shor na /
NK083('u)001:529: ngan dred du song bas don mi 'grub /
NK083('u)001:534: rtsom pa la sogs pa'i blo ru song na /
NK083('u)001:536: des na de gnyis ka dang blo ma dred par /
NK083('u)001:537: gang bsgrub pa de nyid la shes pa rtse gcig tu phur tshugs su dril te /
NK083('u)001:541: chad med gsal ba'i sdug sran byed //
NK083('u)001:542: dka' thub sa rdo btsugs nas snying rus chen pos
NK083('u)001:543: sgrub pa 'di mthar 'don dgos snyam pa'i sgo nas
NK083('u)001:544: bsgrub pa'o // de yang dang po 'jug pa'i dus su skyabs 'gro bya /
NK083('u)001:545: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed /
NK083('u)001:546: lha yi nga rgyal dang ldan par byas la /
NK083('u)001:548: dang po bla ma dang dkon mchog la phul gsol ba gdab /
NK083('u)001:549: bar pa chos skyong la phul la bar chad ma btang zhig bar phrin las gzhol /
NK083('u)001:550: tha ma gzhi bdag la phul la gnas bo zhu /
NK083('u)001:551: de nas rang dang gnas dang gnas bdag gsum po mi dmigs pa'i ngang la bzhag go //
NK083('u)001:553: sgo drung du tho dkar po gcig brtsigs /
NK083('u)001:554: bar chad mi 'byung ba'i rten 'brel yin /
NK083('u)001:555: mal 'og tu sa dkar po'i g.yung drung ris bya /
NK083('u)001:560: 'dun pa skyed la mtshams dam por bcad pas bar
NK083('u)001:561: chad mi 'byung zhing myur du 'grub pa yin no
NK083('u)001:562: // nyin mo snang ba bzo med lhug par bzhag /srod la rig pa gzings bstod la /
NK083('u)001:563: ma bying ma rmugs par seng nge yer re bzhag go //
NK083('u)001:564: nam gung gnyid dang chos nyid bsres la rtog med du nyal /
NK083('u)001:565: tho rangs dran pa gsal btab la lha'i nga rgyal gyis ldang /
NK083('u)001:568: sems spros bral la bzhag /dam bca' yun thung la grangs mang bar bslab bo //
NK083('u)001:570: cho ga gsum ma ma skad cig dran rdzogs las lhar bskyed /
NK083('u)001:572: ru tsi ra ma ni pra brda n+aa ya h'u phata /
NK083('u)001:574: rten 'brel snying po bdun gyis phreng ba byin gyis brlab /
NK083('u)001:585: skyon bdun po de bsal la /
NK083('u)001:588: phreng ba la rig pa gtad nas bazla'o //
NK083('u)001:590: zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhi dkar ser dmar nag go //
NK083('u)001:593: tshur 'dus pas dngos grub thob pa'o //
NK083('u)001:596: mi tshig gis bar mi bcad /
NK083('u)001:597: khyad par bsnyen pa'i dus su chod na bsnyen pa'i go mi chod /
NK083('u)001:606: am +aah ka kha ga g+ha nga /
NK083('u)001:612: sha sha sa ha k+shah 'grub par gyur cig s+w+aa h+aa //
NK083('u)001:616: byin rlabs che ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:618: mtshon rtse kha ru mi 'jug /mchil ma phyir mi 'dor /
NK083('u)001:621: lha yin no snyam pa ni don spyi yin /
NK083('u)001:622: sems nyid lha yi ngo bo hril song nas /
NK083('u)001:623: lha dang rig pa dbyer med ni don rang mtshan no //
NK083('u)001:627: sgrub pa ma thon bar la gzhan don mi bya /
NK083('u)001:630: stan mi sprug /gdong pa dang lag pa mi bkru /
NK083('u)001:631: skra dang kha spu mi 'dreg /thon pa dang dngos grub blang /
NK083('u)001:635: gnyis pa bsrung ba'i 'khor lo ni /
NK083('u)001:636: rnal 'byor bsrung ba'i 'khor lo'i rim pa ni //
NK083('u)001:639: sgrub pa byed pa la bar chad 'ong bas /
NK083('u)001:640: de dag srung ba'i 'khor lo la drug las /
NK083('u)001:641: dang po byang chub sems kyi srung bya ni /
NK083('u)001:642: lus can rnams kyi byang chub mchog thob bsgom //
NK083('u)001:646: khyad par bdag la gnod byed kyi gtsos byas pa'i sems can thams cad bde ba dang ldan /
NK083('u)001:648: sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi go 'phang thob par bya /
NK083('u)001:652: lus ngag yid gsum dge ba la bkol snyam du sems bskyed /
NK083('u)001:653: de ni bsrung ba kun gyi mchog yin te /
NK083('u)001:654: gnod byed kho rang gi don du sgrub pa byed pa la /
NK083('u)001:655: kho rang gis bar du mi gcod pas so //
NK083('u)001:656: gnyis pa mtshon cha lnga'i srung ba ni /
NK083('u)001:657: lha mtshan rdo rje 'khor lo mtshon mes bsrung //
NK083('u)001:659: rang skad cig ma'i ngang la yi dam lha gang yin du bsgom /
NK083('u)001:660: de'i thugs kar rtsa ba'i sa bon yig 'bru bsam /
NK083('u)001:661: thugs ka'i yig 'bru las yi dam gang yin gyi
NK083('u)001:662: phyag mtshan 'od zer dang bcas pa phar 'phros pas
NK083('u)001:664: tshur 'dus pas steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad phyag
NK083('u)001:665: mtshan rtse mo phyir bstan pa'i gur du bsam mo
NK083('u)001:666: // yang thugs ka'i yig 'bru las rdo rje 'od zer dang bcas pa phar 'phros /
NK083('u)001:667: 'dus pas thams cad rdo rje'i gur du bsam mo //
NK083('u)001:668: yang sa bon las 'khor lo 'od zer dang bcas
NK083('u)001:669: pa 'phros 'dus pa las thams cad 'khor lo'i gur
NK083('u)001:670: du bsam / yang sa bon las mtshon cha sna
NK083('u)001:671: tshogs 'phros 'dus pas thams cad mtshon cha'i gur du
NK083('u)001:672: du bsam / bsam mo // yang sa bon las
NK083('u)001:673: me'i 'od zer 'phros 'dus pas thams cad me'i gur
NK083('u)001:675: 'di ni 'khor g.yog srung ba la zab bo //
NK083('u)001:676: gsum pa yig 'bru gsum gyi srung ba ni /
NK083('u)001:677: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs yig bsgom //
NK083('u)001:679: rang gi lus sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku'i rang bzhin dkar po gcig tu bsam /
NK083('u)001:680: de je cher gyur pa'i nang du /
NK083('u)001:681: ngag sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gsung gi rang bzhin +aahdamara po gcig tu bsam /
NK083('u)001:682: de je cher gyur pa'i nang du /
NK083('u)001:683: sems sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs kyi rang bzhin h'u mthing nag gcig tu gyur par bsam /
NK083('u)001:684: de ltar lus ngag sems gsum sku gsung thugs kyi yi ger gyur par bsam pa la /
NK083('u)001:685: bar du gcod pa med de 'di ni rang nyid kho na'o //
NK083('u)001:686: bzhi pa zhi drag sum brtsegs kyi bsrung ba ni /
NK083('u)001:687: spyan ras 'jam dpal gang yin yi dam bsgom /
NK083('u)001:689: rang gang bsrung ba tsam khyab par 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs su bsgoms /
NK083('u)001:690: de ni zhi ba'i rang bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:691: de'i thugs kar 'jam dpal khros pa gshin rje gshed bsgom /
NK083('u)001:692: de ni khro bo'i rang bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:693: de'i thugs kar rang yi dam gang yin du bsgom /
NK083('u)001:694: de ni gnyis su med pa'iranga bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:695: de ltar zhi drag dbyer med du gnas pa la /
NK083('u)001:696: bar du gcod pa med de /
NK083('u)001:697: 'di ni yul dang lung bsrung na zab bo //
NK083('u)001:698: lnga pa rang byung lhun gyis grub pa'i bsrung ba ni /
NK083('u)001:699: rdo rje'i sa rwa gur dang mda' me bsgom //
NK083('u)001:701: rkang mthil rdo rje'i sa gzhi /
NK083('u)001:702: rtsibs ma rdo rje'i rwa ba /
NK083('u)001:704: skra dang ba spu mad'i ra ba /
NK083('u)001:705: so dang sen mo me rab tu 'bar bar bsgom /
NK083('u)001:706: de rnams ni de ltar yin snyam du shes shing dran pas chog ste /
NK083('u)001:707: 'di ni rang bsrung ba la zab bo //
NK083('u)001:708: drug pa don dam mtshan ma med pas bsrung ba ni /
NK083('u)001:709: bya byed ngo bo mi dmigs ngang la bzhag /ces pas /
NK083('u)001:712: bar chad rang gi ngo bo dang gsum /
NK083('u)001:713: dbyer med spros bral mi dmigs pa'i ngo bor shes shing /
NK083('u)001:714: stong nyid kyi ngang la bzhag go //
NK083('u)001:715: de la gang gis kyang bar du mi chod de /
NK083('u)001:716: stong pa la stong pas glags mi rnyed pa'o //
NK083('u)001:717: de rnams kyang sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i nub mo dang /
NK083('u)001:719: srod kyi thun 'gor byang sems kyi srung ba dang /
NK083('u)001:720: mtshon me'i srung ba gang 'grub bya'o //
NK083('u)001:722: gnad lnga'i sgo nas lam la 'jug pa ni /
NK083('u)001:724: gnad lnga'i sgo nas theg chen gyi lam la 'jug pa la lnga ste /
NK083('u)001:725: skyabs 'gros chos kyi gzhi bca' ba /
NK083('u)001:726: yi ge brgya pa bgrang la sgrib pa sbyang ba /
NK083('u)001:727: las 'bras dang mi rtag pa bsgom la blo sbyang ba /
NK083('u)001:728: man+dala dang gtor ma btang la tshogs bsags pa /
NK083('u)001:729: mchod pa phul la tshogs yongs su spel ba'o //
NK083('u)001:731: skyabs 'gro thun mong khyad par bla med gsum skyabs 'gro /
NK083('u)001:737: spyir bstan pa la lnga las /
NK083('u)001:738: dang po skyabs su 'gro ba'i yul ni /
NK083('u)001:740: skyob pa'i nus pa yod cing /
NK083('u)001:741: thugs rje thabs la mkhas pa'i phyir ro //
NK083('u)001:742: gsum gyi dang po sangs rgyas la gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:744: gnas lugs mngon du byas pas /
NK083('u)001:746: 'khrul pa sangs la ye shes rgyas pa /
NK083('u)001:748: chos sku gzugs sku gnyis sam /
NK083('u)001:749: chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum mam /
NK083('u)001:752: gnyis pa chos la gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:761: gsum pa dge 'dun la gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:767: yang dag don gyi dge 'dun no //
NK083('u)001:768: gnyis pa skyabs 'gro gsum po bstan pa'i ngo bor bstan pa ni /
NK083('u)001:769: chos kyi bsgrub bya sangs rgyas yin pa dang /
NK083('u)001:770: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa ston pa chos yin pa dang /
NK083('u)001:771: chos nyams su len pa dge 'dun yin pas bstan pa'i ngo bo yin no //
NK083('u)001:772: gsum pa skyabs 'gro byed pa'i gang zag la gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:774: skyabs su song ma song gi skyon yon shes nas 'jug pa'o //
NK083('u)001:776: rgyu 'bras la yid ches pa'i gang zag go //
NK083('u)001:780: gsang sngags rig pa 'dzin pa'i gang zag go //
NK083('u)001:781: bzhi pa tshul ji ltar skyabs su 'gro ba la gnyis las /
NK083('u)001:783: sangs rgyas la skyabs su song bas /
NK083('u)001:784: 'jig rten pa'i lha la phyag mi 'tshal /
NK083('u)001:785: chos la skyabs su song bas /
NK083('u)001:786: sems can la gnod pa mi bskyal /
NK083('u)001:787: dge 'dun la skyabs su song bas /
NK083('u)001:788: mu stegs pa dang mi 'grogs pa'o //
NK083('u)001:789: khyad par gyi 'gro tshul gsum ni /
NK083('u)001:793: lnga pa skyabs 'gro'i phan yon ni /
NK083('u)001:794: nang pa sangs rgyas kyi khongs su tshud pa /
NK083('u)001:795: sdom pa thams cad kyi rten byed pa /
NK083('u)001:796: mi dang mi ma yin pas mi tshugs pa /
NK083('u)001:798: mthar thug sangs rgyas thob pa'o //
NK083('u)001:799: gnyis pa skyabs 'gro bye brag tu bshad pa gsum /
NK083('u)001:804: thun mong gi skyabs 'gro la gsum las /
NK083('u)001:805: dang po skyabs gnas ngos bzung ba ni /
NK083('u)001:807: sprul pa'i sku kho na dam pa 'dzin te sh+aakya thub pa /
NK083('u)001:809: rgyu'i theg pa bden pa bzhi /
NK083('u)001:810: lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa la gtsor byed /
NK083('u)001:812: phyi'i cha lugs dang spyod lam gyis 'dul ba phyi gzugs rtags kyi dge 'dun no //
NK083('u)001:813: gnyis pa skyabs su 'gro byed kyi gang zag ni /
NK083('u)001:814: nyan thos rang rgyal gnyis so //
NK083('u)001:815: gsum pa skyabs su 'gro tshul ni /
NK083('u)001:817: thun mong gi skyabs 'gro la brten nas so sor thar pa'i sdom pa skye /
NK083('u)001:818: de cho ga'i dus su thob /
NK083('u)001:819: de lam bden pa bzhis sbyangs nas /
NK083('u)001:820: 'bras bu srid pa gsum na dgra bcom pa thob /
NK083('u)001:821: gnyis pa khyad par gyi skyabs 'gro la gsum /
NK083('u)001:822: dang po skyabs gnas ngos bzung ba ni /
NK083('u)001:824: spangs rtogs phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK083('u)001:825: chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum /
NK083('u)001:826: de yang chos sku dag pa gnyis ldan /
NK083('u)001:827: dbyings rang bzhin rnam par dag pa /
NK083('u)001:828: spang bya glo bur gyi dri ma dang bral bas dag pa'o //
NK083('u)001:829: longs sku nges pa lnga ldan /
NK083('u)001:830: sprul sku ma nges pa lnga ldan /
NK083('u)001:832: rgyu yi theg pa don rnam par nges pa'i /
NK083('u)001:834: lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa la gtsor byed /
NK083('u)001:836: gzhan don sems kyi dge 'dun te /
NK083('u)001:837: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa rlabs po che'o //
NK083('u)001:838: gnyis pa skyabs su 'gro byed kyi gang zag ni /
NK083('u)001:839: byang chub sems dpa'i gang zag ste /
NK083('u)001:842: gsum pa skyabs su 'gro tshul ni /
NK083('u)001:843: tshad med pa bzhi'i sgo nas rang gzhan gnyis kyi don byed pa'o //
NK083('u)001:844: khyad par gyi skyabs 'gro de la brten nas byang sems kyi sdom pa skye /
NK083('u)001:845: de sems bskyed kyi dus su thob /
NK083('u)001:846: de lam pha rol tu phyin pa drug la sbyangs nas /
NK083('u)001:847: 'bras bu bskal pa gsum nas sangs rgyas thob bo //
NK083('u)001:848: gsum pa bla na med pa'i skyabs 'gro la gnyis te /
NK083('u)001:852: dang po skyabs gnas ngos bzung ba ni /
NK083('u)001:854: sku lnga dbyer med gcig dang du ma bral ba /
NK083('u)001:858: lung du bstan cing rmad du byung ba /
NK083('u)001:859: bslab pa gsum gang du yang bstan du btub ste /
NK083('u)001:860: gsang sngags kyi chos la gtso bor byed /
NK083('u)001:862: yang dag don gyi dge 'dun te /
NK083('u)001:863: mi dge ba ngang gis mi gnas pa'o //
NK083('u)001:864: gnyis pa skyabs su 'gro byed kyi gang zag ni /
NK083('u)001:865: gsang sngags rig pa 'dzin pa'i rnal 'byor te /
NK083('u)001:867: gsum pa skyabs su 'gro tshul ni /
NK083('u)001:868: rang gzhan gyi lus ngag yid gsum dang /
NK083('u)001:869: dkon mchog gsum dbyer med pas /
NK083('u)001:870: yul dang yul can gnyis med 'agro'o //
NK083('u)001:871: bla med kyi skyabs 'gro de dag la brten nas /
NK083('u)001:872: gsang sngags kyi sdom pa skye ste /
NK083('u)001:873: de dbang gi dus su thob /
NK083('u)001:874: de lam rim pa gnyis kyis sbyangs nas /
NK083('u)001:878: gnyis pa a ti'i skyabs 'gro la gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:879: dang po dkon mchog gsum po ngos bzung ba ni /
NK083('u)001:880: rig pa sku bzhir gnas pa sangs rgyas dkon mchog /de nyid stong pa dbyer med pa'o //
NK083('u)001:881: de shes kyi shes pa chos dkon mchog ste /
NK083('u)001:882: a ti yo ga khyad par rmad du byung ba ste /
NK083('u)001:884: gshis la sdig pa ma grub cing /
NK083('u)001:885: ngo bo zag pa med pa'i dge bar gnas pa ni /
NK083('u)001:886: yang dag don gyi dge 'dun no //
NK083('u)001:887: gnyis pa gang zag ngos bzung ba ni /
NK083('u)001:888: skyes mchog gang zag yang rab a ti'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK083('u)001:889: gsum pa skyabs su 'gro tshul la gsum /
NK083('u)001:890: dkon mchog rang gi sems la grub par shes pa ni /
NK083('u)001:892: rang gi sems ma yin pa'i dkon mchog gsum med par rtogs pa ni /
NK083('u)001:894: sems nyid dkon mchog gi rang bzhin gcig dang du ma bral zhing /
NK083('u)001:895: mtha' gang la yang mi gnas pa /
NK083('u)001:896: gnyis med rang grol du rtogs pa ni /
NK083('u)001:897: yang dag bla med kyi skyabs 'agro'o //
NK083('u)001:898: des na sangs rgyas kyi bka' bzhin du bsgrub cing gsung na bla ma yin /
NK083('u)001:899: de'i gsung bzhin bsgrub na slob ma yin /
NK083('u)001:900: de'i cha rkyen bsgrub na yon bdag yin /
NK083('u)001:901: de lta bu gang na yod pa de na sangs rgyas bstan pa yod do //
NK083('u)001:902: gnyis pa yi ge brgya pas sgrib pa sbyong ba ni /
NK083('u)001:903: dkar dmar nag gsum brgya bzlas mchod dang bskang //
NK083('u)001:905: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed /
NK083('u)001:906: de nas rang yi dam lha ru bsgom /
NK083('u)001:907: de'i thugs kar sa bon gyi yig 'bru gcig la /
NK083('u)001:908: yi ge brgya ba dkar dmar nag gsum gyis bskor bar bsam la /
NK083('u)001:909: badz+ra sa t+wa sa ma ya /
NK083('u)001:911: badz+ra sa t+wa de no pa tish+tha /
NK083('u)001:913: su to sh+yo me b+ha wa /
NK083('u)001:914: su po sh+yo me b+ha wa /
NK083('u)001:915: a nu rak+to me b+ha wa /
NK083('u)001:917: sarba karma su tsa me tsit+tam sh+re ya ku ru h'u /
NK083('u)001:918: ha ha ha ha hoh b+ha ga w+aan sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra m+aa me muny+tsa /
NK083('u)001:920: ma h+aa sa ma ya sa t+wa a /
NK083('u)001:922: yi ge brgya pa dkar po las 'od dkar po 'phros /
NK083('u)001:923: bde gshegs sku la mchod pa phul /
NK083('u)001:924: sems can thams cad kyi lus kyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK083('u)001:925: sku'i dam tshig nyams pa bskangs par bsam /
NK083('u)001:926: brgya pa dmar po las 'od dmar po 'phros pas /
NK083('u)001:927: bde gshegs gsung la mchod pa phul /
NK083('u)001:928: rang gzhan sems can thams cad kyi ngag gi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK083('u)001:929: gsung gi dam tshigs nyams pa thams cad bskangs par bsam /
NK083('u)001:930: brgya pa nag po las 'od zer nag po 'phros pas /
NK083('u)001:931: bde gshegs thugs la mchod pa phul /
NK083('u)001:932: rang gzhan sems can thams cad kyi yid kyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK083('u)001:933: thugs kyi dam tshig nyams pa thams cad bskangs bar bsam mo //
NK083('u)001:934: de nas rang nyid 'od du zhu nas yig 'brur gyur /
NK083('u)001:935: yi ge skye med stong nyid mi dmigs pa'i ngang la bzhag go //
NK083('u)001:937: de nas bargya'am nyer gcig la sogs pa gang 'grub re bgrang /
NK083('u)001:938: des sdig sgrib thams cad dag /nyams chag thams cad bskang ngo //
NK083('u)001:940: 'chi ba mi rtag pa bsgom la blo sbyong ba ni /
NK083('u)001:941: dal 'byor las 'bras mi rtag nyes dmigs bsgom //
NK083('u)001:944: dang po dal 'byor rnyed par dka' ba bsgom pa ni /
NK083('u)001:945: byang chub sgrub pa'i rten ni /
NK083('u)001:947: dal ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK083('u)001:948: mi khoms pa'i gnas brgyad dang bral ba la bya ste /
NK083('u)001:950: dmyal ba yi dwags dud 'gro dang //
NK083('u)001:951: tshe ring lha dang kla klo dang //
NK083('u)001:952: sangs rgyas mi 'byung log lta dang //
NK083('u)001:953: lkugs pa 'di dag mi khoms brgyad //
NK083('u)001:955: ngan song gsum dang lha tshe ring po ste /
NK083('u)001:956: mi ma yin pa'i 'gro ba bzhi dang /
NK083('u)001:957: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa med pa'i sa dang /
NK083('u)001:958: yod kyang ma khyab pa'i mtha'i kla klo dang /
NK083('u)001:959: las 'bras med ces log par lta ba dang /
NK083('u)001:960: 'on long dig lkugs la sogs pa dbang po ma tshang ba'i mis bsdus pa bzhi ste brgyad do //
NK083('u)001:961: skyon bzhi gnyis brgyad po de dang bral ba ni dal ba ste /
NK083('u)001:962: chos khyad par can gyi rten du rung ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:964: mir gyur yul gyi dbus skyes dang //
NK083('u)001:965: dbang po tshang zhing gnas la dad //
NK083('u)001:966: de bzhin las mtha' ma log pa'o //
NK083('u)001:968: mi nyid du gyur pa dang /
NK083('u)001:969: yul dbus su skyes pa dang /
NK083('u)001:971: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i gnas la dad pa dang /
NK083('u)001:972: las kyi mtha' ma log pa ste rang 'byor lnga dang /
NK083('u)001:973: sangs rgyas rnams byon chos gsungs dang //
NK083('u)001:974: bstan pa gnas dang de rjes 'jug /gzhan phyir snying rje lnga yin no //
NK083('u)001:976: sangs rgyas 'jig rten du byon pa /
NK083('u)001:978: bstan pa de yun du gnas pa /
NK083('u)001:980: gzhan gyi phyir brtse ba'i thugs rje yod pa ste gzhan 'byor lnga'o //
NK083('u)001:981: de ltar yon tan lnga gnyis bcu dang ldan pa de ni 'byor ba ces bya ste /
NK083('u)001:982: chos la spyad du yod pa'o //
NK083('u)001:983: de ni rgyu rkyen ngo bo gang la brtags kyang thob pa shin tu dka' ba yin pas /
NK083('u)001:984: de ltar bsgom na 'khor ba la blo ldog pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:985: gnyis pa las rgyu 'bras la gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:986: las kyi ngo bo ngos bzung ba dang /
NK083('u)001:990: las kyi ngo bo ngos bzung ba /
NK083('u)001:991: gang nyes par spyod pa dngos sam brgyud nas sdug
NK083('u)001:992: bsngal bskyed pa ni sdig pa ste mi dge ba'i
NK083('u)001:993: las so // de la gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:994: rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho ba /
NK083('u)001:995: spyad pa nyid na sdig tu gyur pa /
NK083('u)001:999: bcas pa'i kha na ma tho ba /
NK083('u)001:1000: bcas pa nyid na ltung bar gyur pa /
NK083('u)001:1001: sdom pa gsum gyi nyes pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1002: 'jig rten gyi kha na ma tho ba /
NK083('u)001:1003: gzhan gyi sdig can byed pa ste /
NK083('u)001:1008: gang legs pa spyod pa dngos sam brgyud nas bde ba skyed pa na dge ba'o //
NK083('u)001:1010: 'khor gsum dmigs pa dang bcas nas gtong ba bsod nams cha mthun dge ba /
NK083('u)001:1011: nges 'byung gi sems kyis kun nas blangs nas gtong ba thar pa cha mthun gyi dge ba /
NK083('u)001:1012: 'khor gsum yongs dag mi dmigs par shes pa thar pa bla na med pa'i dge ba'o //
NK083('u)001:1013: dge sdig gnyis ka ma yin pa ni /
NK083('u)001:1014: lung ma bstan gyi las so //
NK083('u)001:1015: gnyis pa las kyi so mtshams dbye ba la bdun las /
NK083('u)001:1016: dang po /1 don gyi dge ba gnas lugs 'dus ma byas /
NK083('u)001:1017: don gyi mi dge ba 'dus byas 'khor ba'i chos so //
NK083('u)001:1018: 5rang bzhin gyis dge ba rig pa ye shes /
NK083('u)001:1019: rang bzhin gyis mi dge ba nyon mongs dug lnga'o //
NK083('u)001:1020: 3gshis dge ba chos nyid stong pa /
NK083('u)001:1021: gshis mi dge ba ma rig pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1022: 4 yang dag pa'i dge ba blo las 'das pa /
NK083('u)001:1023: yang dag pa'i mi dge ba yid kyis bslad pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1024: 2yid la mi byed pa ni myang 'das te dge ba /
NK083('u)001:1025: yid la byed pa ni 'khor ba de mi dge ba'o //
NK083('u)001:1026: 6dug gsum cha phra mos spags pa'i dge bas mtho ris gsum /
NK083('u)001:1027: dug gsum gyis kun nas bslangs pa'i sdig pas ngan song gsum bskyed do //
NK083('u)001:1028: 7 thabs shes kyi dge bas mi gnas pa'i myang 'das /
NK083('u)001:1029: thabs shes ci rigs pa'i dge bas phyogs gcig pa'i myang 'das so //
NK083('u)001:1030: gsum pa las gyi rnam grangs la /
NK083('u)001:1035: 'dres pa'i las dge sdig 'dres pa ste /
NK083('u)001:1037: bsam pa dkar la sbyor ba gnag pa /
NK083('u)001:1038: mi nag mdung thung can bsad pa lta bu'o //
NK083('u)001:1039: bsam pa nag la sbyor ba dkar ba /
NK083('u)001:1040: gsod pa'i phyir bsnyen bkur byed pa lta bu'o //
NK083('u)001:1041: bsam sbyor gnyis ka dkar ba /
NK083('u)001:1042: sangs rgyas thob pa'i phyir dge ba la sbyor ba lta bu'o //
NK083('u)001:1044: zhe sdang gis bsad pa lta bu /
NK083('u)001:1046: tshe 'dir rnam smin myong ba'i las so //
NK083('u)001:1048: skye ba phyi ma la myong nges /
NK083('u)001:1049: lan grangs gzhan la myong ba /
NK083('u)001:1050: skye ba gsum phan la myong ba'i las so //
NK083('u)001:1051: las dkar rnam smin dkar ba /
NK083('u)001:1052: dge ba byas pas bde 'gro skye ba'o //
NK083('u)001:1053: las nag rnam smin nag pa /
NK083('u)001:1054: mi dge ba byas pas ngan 'gror skye ba'o //
NK083('u)001:1055: las dkar rnam smin nag pa /
NK083('u)001:1056: mi sdug bsngal can lta bu /
NK083('u)001:1057: las nag rnam smin dkar ba /
NK083('u)001:1059: 'phen byed dge ba la rdzogs byed kyang dge ba /
NK083('u)001:1061: 'phel byed dge ba la rdzogs byed mi dge ba /
NK083('u)001:1063: 'phen byed kyang mi dge ba la rdzogs byed kyang mi dge ba /
NK083('u)001:1064: dud 'gror skye ba'i sdug bsngal can lta bu /
NK083('u)001:1065: 'phel byed mi dge ba la rdzogs byed dge ba'i las klu phyug po lta bu /
NK083('u)001:1067: bdag gis mi dge ba byas pa'i las gzhan la mi smin /
NK083('u)001:1068: gzhan gyis dge mi dge byas pa bdag la mi smin /
NK083('u)001:1069: rang gis las ma byas pa dang mi 'phrad /
NK083('u)001:1070: rang gi dge sdig byas pa'i las chud mi za /
NK083('u)001:1071: dge mi dge /dkar nag gi las mi 'chol bas /
NK083('u)001:1072: de'i phyir sdug bsngal myong ba'i las dge ba dang mi dge ba /
NK083('u)001:1073: shin tu phra ba nas 'dor len bya'o //
NK083('u)001:1074: gsum pa mi rtag pa bsgom pa la gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:1075: skyes phan chad 'chi nges par 'dug /de ka mi
NK083('u)001:1076: rtag pa'i ngo bo yin par 'dug /don snying la
NK083('u)001:1077: mtshon phog pa'i skyes bu dang 'dra /
NK083('u)001:1078: de yang nam 'chi nges pa mi 'dug /de ka mi rtag pa'i mtshan nyid yin te /
NK083('u)001:1080: 'chi ba la cis kyang mi phan par 'dug /de ka mi rtag pa'i khyad chos yin te /
NK083('u)001:1081: nyi ma rgas pa'i grib so dang 'dra'o //
NK083('u)001:1082: dang po 'chi nges pa la rgyu mtshan gsum /
NK083('u)001:1083: sngar skyes pa lus pa med pa dang /
NK083('u)001:1084: tshe la bsnon pa med cing 'brid pa yod pa dang /
NK083('u)001:1085: lus sems 'dus byas yin te 'chi nges pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1086: gnyis pa nam 'chi nges pa med pa la yang rgyu mtshan gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:1087: tshe la dus btab med pa dang /
NK083('u)001:1089: 'dus byas 'jig pa'i rang bzhin can yin pas nam 'chi nges pa med do //
NK083('u)001:1090: gsum pa 'chi ba la cis kyang mi phan pa la'ang rgyu mtshan gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:1093: brtsigs pa'i mkhar gyis mi phan pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1094: de ltar mi rtag pa bsgoms pas 'jig rten 'di la blo ldog pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:1095: bzhi pa 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs bsgom pa ni /
NK083('u)001:1097: khams gsum kyi sems can yin la /
NK083('u)001:1098: de dag ni sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin /
NK083('u)001:1100: sdug bsngal gyi yo lang yin te /
NK083('u)001:1101: rtsa ba'i sdug bsngal bzhi ni /
NK083('u)001:1104: yan lag gi sdug bsngal drug ni /
NK083('u)001:1106: bud pa dang sangs pa med /
NK083('u)001:1107: nying lag gi sdug bsngal ni /
NK083('u)001:1108: gnam gyi skar ma dang 'dra ste /
NK083('u)001:1110: des na gang du skyes kyang sdug bsngal gyi yo lang /
NK083('u)001:1111: su dang 'grogs kyang sdug bsngal gyi grogs po /
NK083('u)001:1112: gang du phyin kyang sdug bsngal gyi gnas po //
NK083('u)001:1113: gang gi yin kyang sdug bsngal gyi bsnon par 'dug ste /
NK083('u)001:1114: lo ka'i phun sum tshogs pa thams cad sdug bsngal gyi rgyu /
NK083('u)001:1115: ma tshogs pa thams cad sdug bsngal gyi 'bras bu ste /
NK083('u)001:1116: sdug bsngal lu gu brgyud dang 'dra ba /
NK083('u)001:1118: chu'i gnyer ma dang 'dra ste bud pa dang sangs pa med /
NK083('u)001:1119: gnam gyi skar ma dang 'dra ste grangs dang tshad med do //
NK083('u)001:1122: myong ba lus kyi sdug bsngal /
NK083('u)001:1123: snang ba yul gyi sdug bsngal /
NK083('u)001:1124: sgo gsum rtsol sgrub kyi sdug bsngal te /
NK083('u)001:1125: sdug bsngal med pa gcig kyang med do //
NK083('u)001:1126: de ltar bsam tsa na 'khor ba 'di la blo ldog pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:1127: bzhi pa man+dala dang gtor mas tshogs gsog pa la gnyis las /
NK083('u)001:1128: dang po man+dala dbul ba ni /
NK083('u)001:1129: sgrub dang mchod pa'i man+dala gnyis su 'bul //
NK083('u)001:1131: sgrub pa'i man+dala dgod pa dang /
NK083('u)001:1135: man+dala phyis pas stong pa nyid du bsam /
NK083('u)001:1136: stong pa'i ngang las gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi rgyan rta babs dang bcas pa bsam /
NK083('u)001:1137: de'i phyogs bzhi dbus dang lngar /
NK083('u)001:1138: seng ge'i khri rin po ches spras pa /
NK083('u)001:1139: nyi zla pad+ma dang bcas pa'i gdan lnga bsam /
NK083('u)001:1140: khri dbus ma'i steng na rtsa ba'i bla ma /
NK083('u)001:1144: byang du dge 'dun dkon mchog gsum /
NK083('u)001:1146: rtsa ba'i bla ma la bka' brgyud kyi bla ma thams cad bstim /
NK083('u)001:1147: yi dam la gsang sngags kyi lha tshogs /
NK083('u)001:1148: sangs rgyas la sku gsum ye shes lnga phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas /
NK083('u)001:1149: chos la bstan sgrub 'gogs pa'i chos thams cad /
NK083('u)001:1150: dge 'dun la nyan rang byang chub sems kyi dge 'dun dpag tu med pa bstim /
NK083('u)001:1151: de rnams la lus longs spyod dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad dbul /
NK083('u)001:1152: mchod pa'i sprin tshogs dpag tu med pas mchod la /
NK083('u)001:1154: bla ma yi dam jo bo dkon mchog bzhes shig
NK083('u)001:1155: /bdag gi lus longs spyod dge rtsa thams cad yongs
NK083('u)001:1157: bla ma yi dam lha tshogs dkon mchog gsum po //
NK083('u)001:1158: bdag la rtogs pa mchog tu gyur pa /
NK083('u)001:1159: nyams myong rgyun chad med pa /
NK083('u)001:1160: snang ba rten 'brel du 'char bar byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK083('u)001:1161: ces gsol ba lan gsum gdab /
NK083('u)001:1162: de nas rten 'khor lo lnga po mdun gyi nam mkha' la btegs la /
NK083('u)001:1163: sarba gu ru lo ka p+au tsa d+harma ye s+w+aa h+aa //
NK083('u)001:1165: gnyis pa mchod pa'i man+dala dbul ba ni /
NK083('u)001:1166: man+dala de phyis bas rgya mtsho sngo la dwangs pa gcig tu bsam /
NK083('u)001:1167: de'i dbus su tshom bu gcig bkod pas /
NK083('u)001:1168: dbus kyi ri rab rgyu rin po che sna tshogs
NK083('u)001:1169: las grub pa dbyibs gru bzhi bang rim lnga dang
NK083('u)001:1170: ldan pa / rgya che la dpang mtho ba gcig bsam /
NK083('u)001:1171: shar du tshom bu gcig bkod pas /
NK083('u)001:1172: lus 'phags po dung las grub pa dbyibs zla gam rgya che la dpang mtho ba gcig bsam /
NK083('u)001:1174: 'dzam bu gling bee d+aur+ya las grub pa dbyibs sog ga /nub tu gcig bkod pas /
NK083('u)001:1175: ba glang spyod shel dmar po las grub pa zlum po /
NK083('u)001:1177: sgra mi snyan gser las grub pa gru bzhi //
NK083('u)001:1178: shar dang dbus kyi bar du gcig bkod la /
NK083('u)001:1179: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor chu shel las grub pa rgya che ba dpang mtho ba gcig bsam /
NK083('u)001:1180: nub dang dbus kyi bar du gcig bkod la /
NK083('u)001:1181: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor me shel las grub pa gcig bsam /
NK083('u)001:1182: de rnams kyi bar thams cad mchod pa'i sprin sna tshogs gcal du bkram pa /
NK083('u)001:1183: rat+na sna tshogs kyis phyur lud du bkang ba /
NK083('u)001:1184: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam par dag pa /
NK083('u)001:1185: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpas gang ba /
NK083('u)001:1186: lha'i bu dang bu mo mang po glu len cing
NK083('u)001:1187: gar bsgyur ba dang bcas pa dmigs la dbul lo
NK083('u)001:1188: // rang gi lus longs spyod dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad ltos pa med par dbul lo //
NK083('u)001:1189: gnyis pa gtor ma skyong ba ni /
NK083('u)001:1190: sna tshogs lam khyer gtor mas tshogs gnyis bsags //
NK083('u)001:1194: btangs thabs bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1195: dang po gnad spyir bstan pa la lnga ste /
NK083('u)001:1202: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa ste /
NK083('u)001:1203: chos nyid stong pa'i rtsal chos can gtor mar 'char ba'o //
NK083('u)001:1208: rtog med ye shes kyi rol pas mgron bzhi tshims pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1209: gsum pa rnam grangs la lnga ste /
NK083('u)001:1210: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang snang 'dzin med
NK083('u)001:1211: du rtogs nas nyon mongs ye shes su shar ba
NK083('u)001:1212: ni / 'gyur med ye shes kyi gtor ma /
NK083('u)001:1213: chos thams cad rang snang gnyis med du rtogs nas sdug bsngal bde bar 'char ba ni /
NK083('u)001:1214: bde chen byang chub sems kyi gtor ma /
NK083('u)001:1215: phyi nang snod bcud sems kyis khyab tshad chos nyid kyis khyab pa ni /
NK083('u)001:1216: yongs su khyab pa'i gtor ma /
NK083('u)001:1217: chos nyid byang chub sems ma byung ma skyes pa ni /
NK083('u)001:1218: dag pa chos nyid kyi gtor ma //
NK083('u)001:1219: thams cad yang dag gnyis med kyi lam du 'gro ba ni /
NK083('u)001:1220: sna tshogs lam khyer gyi gtor ma'o //
NK083('u)001:1221: bzhi pa mgron ngos bzung ba la gnyis las /
NK083('u)001:1224: dang po phyi mtshan nyid ltar na /
NK083('u)001:1225: srid zhi'i mgron yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la nyan rang byang sems kyis bskor ba'am /
NK083('u)001:1226: yum chen mo shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin
NK083('u)001:1227: ma la sras phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis bskor ba'o
NK083('u)001:1228: // yon tan gyi mgron gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje la gtsang ris mgon pos bskor ba /
NK083('u)001:1229: snying rje'i mgron 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs la rigs drug sems can gyis bskor ba /
NK083('u)001:1230: lan chags kyi mgron dpal rta mgrin la bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cus bskor ba'o //
NK083('u)001:1231: gnyis pa nang gsang sngags ltar na /
NK083('u)001:1232: srid zhi'i mgron bla ma yi dam zhi khro'i lha tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK083('u)001:1233: yon tan mkha' 'gro sde lnga la chos skyong pho mos bskor ba /
NK083('u)001:1234: snying rje dus gsum pha ma rigs drug sems can gyis bskor ba /
NK083('u)001:1235: lan chags rang gi srung ma la lha srin sde brgyad kyis bskor ba'o //
NK083('u)001:1236: lnga pa gtor ma'i de nyid la bzhi ste /
NK083('u)001:1243: rtags sngags dang phyag rgya ting nge 'dzin yig 'bru'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK083('u)001:1244: gnyis pa gtor ma'i dgongs pa bzhi ni /
NK083('u)001:1245: bdag yi dam lhar gsal ba /
NK083('u)001:1246: gnas gzhal yas khang du gsal ba /
NK083('u)001:1247: mgron rnams lha pho mor gsal ba //
NK083('u)001:1248: rdzas bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor gsal ba'o //
NK083('u)001:1249: gtor ma'i spyod lam bzhi ni /
NK083('u)001:1250: 'bags pa dang rtsog pa med pa /
NK083('u)001:1251: bo ba dang zags pa med pa /
NK083('u)001:1252: dngos po bzang zhing dri mas ma gos pa /
NK083('u)001:1253: sems ma g.yengs shing ting nge 'dzin gsal ba'o //
NK083('u)001:1254: gsum pa gtor ma'i las bzhi ni /
NK083('u)001:1259: gtor ma'i rim pa bzhi ni /
NK083('u)001:1260: sgrub pa'i gtor ma bskyil bas dam can 'dus pa /
NK083('u)001:1261: rgyun gtor btang bas las myur ba /
NK083('u)001:1262: dus gtor dang skong gtor ma chag pas bsam pa 'grub pa /
NK083('u)001:1263: drag po'i gtor ma zor du 'phangs pas dgra bgegs thul ba'o //
NK083('u)001:1264: bzhi pa gtor ma'i de nyid ma shes pa'i skyon ni /
NK083('u)001:1265: chu ma blugs na spel bar mi nus /
NK083('u)001:1266: byin gyis ma brlabs na rgyal ba dang dam tshig nyams /
NK083('u)001:1267: bsngo ba log na sgrib pa gsog /ma 'byor na lung skam gyi ri dwags su skye /
NK083('u)001:1268: rgyu rkyen ma tshang na mgron mi 'tshogs /
NK083('u)001:1269: mgron ma 'tshogs na btang ba'i 'bras bu med /
NK083('u)001:1270: rdzas ma tshogs na spyan drangs kyang mi 'byon /
NK083('u)001:1271: dam rdzas ngo ma shes na lha'i chad pa 'ong /
NK083('u)001:1272: cho ga gzhung ma bsrang na srung ma'i chad pa'onga /
NK083('u)001:1273: ma btang na bsam pa mi 'grub /
NK083('u)001:1274: sgrub pa ma thon bar la gtor gzhong bshal na chos skyong mi 'du /
NK083('u)001:1275: gtor gzhong kha phyir bstan nas pho na dngos grub
NK083('u)001:1276: log /gtor ma gtod khar ma sgul na len mi
NK083('u)001:1277: nus so // de nyid shes pa'i yon tan ni /
NK083('u)001:1278: chu blugs pas spel bar nus /
NK083('u)001:1279: byin gyis brlabs pas rgyal ba dang dam tshig mi
NK083('u)001:1280: nyams pa la sogs pa skyon de dag las log
NK083('u)001:1282: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK083('u)001:1285: dang po lam khyer la bzhi ste /
NK083('u)001:1289: de kho na nyid kyi gtor ma'o //

NK083('u)001:1679: phyogs bcu'i khams bkang rgyas par 'bul //
NK083('u)001:1680: a la la ste bzhes su gsol //
NK083('u)001:1682: snod kyi lo ka phyogs bcu'i khams thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam par dag pa /
NK083('u)001:1686: ye shes rin po che'i khang pa /
NK083('u)001:1687: ri thams cad rin po che'i phung po /
NK083('u)001:1688: chu thams cad khrus kyi rdzing bu /
NK083('u)001:1689: shing thams cad dpag bsam gyi shing /
NK083('u)001:1690: sgra thams cad glu dang dbyangs dang tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra /
NK083('u)001:1691: gos thams cad bla re dang //
NK083('u)001:1695: rdzas thams cad bza' ba dang btung ba'i mchog /
NK083('u)001:1696: 'gro ba thams cad lha dang lha mo /
NK083('u)001:1699: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams gang bar bsam la dbul lo //
NK083('u)001:1700: bzhi pa gsang ba'i mchod pa gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:1701: 'khrul snang gzhi med du bstan pa la sgrol mchod /
NK083('u)001:1702: thabs shes zung 'brel du bstan pa la sbyor mchod //
NK083('u)001:1703: gshis mnyam pa nyid du bstan pa la 'dod yon gyi mchod pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1705: 'khrul snang gzhi med du bstan pa /
NK083('u)001:1706: gnyis 'dzin mtshan ma'i chos rnams la //
NK083('u)001:1707: ngo bo cir yang grub pa med //
NK083('u)001:1708: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK083('u)001:1709: gnyis su med pa'i mchod pa bzhes //
NK083('u)001:1711: gnyis 'dzin 'khrul ba mtshan ma'i chos thams cad la
NK083('u)001:1712: ngo bo bden par grub pa cir yang med pas
NK083('u)001:1713: / gnas lugs stong pa nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin /
NK083('u)001:1714: spros bral bde ba chen po chos kyi sku rang byung gi ye shes yin la /
NK083('u)001:1716: mchod pa thams cad kyi nang nas mchog tu gyur pa yin te /
NK083('u)001:1717: gnyis 'dzin 'khrul pa'i snang ba 'di gnyis med ye shes su grol bas na sgrol mchod do //
NK083('u)001:1719: thabs shes zung 'brel du bstan pa /
NK083('u)001:1720: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa //
NK083('u)001:1721: bde chen spros bral thig le'i sku //
NK083('u)001:1722: ye nas gnas pa don gyi mchog /
NK083('u)001:1725: chos thams cad kyi gshis cir yang ma yin par shes pa ni shes rab /
NK083('u)001:1726: de'i gdangs 'gags med du 'char ba ni thabs /
NK083('u)001:1727: de gnyis tha mi dad pas na gnyis su med pa /
NK083('u)001:1728: gnyis med kyi don la mtshan ma'i zug rngu med pas bde ba /
NK083('u)001:1729: de tha mal bde ba las khyad par du gyur pa chen po /
NK083('u)001:1730: gnyis 'dzin gyi zug rngu med pas spros bral /
NK083('u)001:1731: gnyis chos kyi gra zur med pas thig le /
NK083('u)001:1732: yon tan gyi rten byed pas na sku zhes bya ste /
NK083('u)001:1733: de gdod ma nas yod pas ye gnas /
NK083('u)001:1734: yang dag pa'i don nges pas na don gyi chos /
NK083('u)001:1736: tha ma mi 'bul bas na mchod pa'i mchog ste /
NK083('u)001:1737: yang dag gnyis med kyi don la sbyor pas na sbyor mchod do //
NK083('u)001:1739: gshis mnyam pa nyid du bstan pa /
NK083('u)001:1740: mnyam pa'i sgrub rdzas chen po ni //
NK083('u)001:1741: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK083('u)001:1742: bza' bca' btung bgo longs spyod rnams //
NK083('u)001:1743: mi dmigs mnyam pa'i mchod par bzhes //
NK083('u)001:1745: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs bzang ngan che chung med pas mnyam pa'i sgrub rdzas /
NK083('u)001:1746: de ltar shes tsa na 'khor 'das gnyis ma grub pas /
NK083('u)001:1748: de tsam na bza' btung la sogs pa thams cad
NK083('u)001:1749: spyod yul yongs su dag pas na mi dmigs pa
NK083('u)001:1751: de rnams gsang sngags lam gyi sngon 'gro yin //
NK083('u)001:1753: de yan chad lam gyi sngon 'agro'o //
NK083('u)001:1754: gnyis pa lam rang gi ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK083('u)001:1755: thun mong theg pa spyi'i lam /
NK083('u)001:1756: khyad par gsang sngags kyi lam mo //
NK083('u)001:1757: dang po thun mong la gnyis te /
NK083('u)001:1758: bslab pa gsum la lam gzhi bca' ba ni //
NK083('u)001:1760: sems gsum gyis lam gyi kha bsgyur ba'o //
NK083('u)001:1761: dang po bslab gsum la lnga ste /
NK083('u)001:1764: mtshan nyid kyi rang ldog /mtshan gzhi'i skye tshul /
NK083('u)001:1765: gnyen po'i sgo nas rnam grangs su 'gyur tshul lo //
NK083('u)001:1768: mi mthun spong sems mnyam 'jog rang ngo shes //
NK083('u)001:1770: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i mi mthun phyogs thams cad spong zhing /
NK083('u)001:1771: sdom pa ni tshul khrims kyi bslab pa /
NK083('u)001:1772: lam theg pa rang rang sgo nas sems mnyam par
NK083('u)001:1773: 'jog pa'i rigs thams cad ting nge 'dzin gyi bslab
NK083('u)001:1774: pa / theg pa so so'i sgo nas sems rang
NK083('u)001:1775: ngo shes pa'i lta ba thams cad shes rab kyi
NK083('u)001:1779: ngo bo lta sgom spyod pa gsum mo //
NK083('u)001:1782: sh+ai la sa ma ti pradz+ny+aa shik+sha na /
NK083('u)001:1787: bu sh+ai la'i rkyen gyis btsun pa'am /
NK083('u)001:1789: nyes ltung gis ma gos pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1792: ma d+ha ra'i rkyen gyis yid 'dzin pa ste /
NK083('u)001:1797: pa ra m+aar+tha pradz+ny+aa'i rkyen gyis don dam shes pa'i shes rab ste /
NK083('u)001:1800: de ka la sde snod rin po che gsum zhes bya ste /
NK083('u)001:1806: gnod sbyor log zhugs khyad par thabs kyis zin //
NK083('u)001:1808: sems can kun la gnod pa'i sbyor ba las log pa tshul khrims /
NK083('u)001:1809: gnod sbyor las log gi steng du gzhan la phan
NK083('u)001:1810: 'dogs pa'i bya ba la zhugs pa la byang sems
NK083('u)001:1811: kyi sdom pa / gnod sbyor las kyang log /phan 'dogs bya ba la yang zhugs /
NK083('u)001:1812: de yang thabs khyad par can gyis zin pa ni gsang sngags kyi sdom pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1815: bden ba'i don mthong goms 'dres de mi 'da' //zhes pas /
NK083('u)001:1816: sdom gsum gang zag gcig gi rgyud la skyes shing bsrung ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK083('u)001:1817: gnas lugs ma nor bar mthong ba ni shes rab ste gsang sngags so //
NK083('u)001:1818: de goms shing 'dris par byed pa ni ting nge 'dzin te byang sems /
NK083('u)001:1819: de las mi 'da' bar tshul khrims te nyan thos /
NK083('u)001:1822: yar ldan mi 'gal bya ba yin te /
NK083('u)001:1827: de yang so thar nyon mongs spangs /
NK083('u)001:1829: gsang sngags lam du byed pas na rang ldog ma 'dres la /
NK083('u)001:1830: nyon mongs pa rang rgyud pa sdom par gcig pas na dgag dgos yongs rdzogs /
NK083('u)001:1831: nyon mongs pas mi gnod la slar grogs su 'gro bas na yon tan yar ldan /
NK083('u)001:1832: sdom lugs dang srung lugs tha dad kyang nyon mongs
NK083('u)001:1833: pa mi dge ba thams cad sdom par gcig pas
NK083('u)001:1834: na sdom gsum gnad kyis mi 'gal bas so //
NK083('u)001:1835: spyi la log nas mkhar brtsigs pa bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:1836: sdom gsum rgyud thog gcig tu bsrung du mi btung ste /
NK083('u)001:1837: so thar dngos po gtso ba'i phyir pags rim dang
NK083('u)001:1838: po 'das nas 'chor bar bshad pas so snyam na
NK083('u)001:1840: de ni thabs mi mkhas shing shes rab chung ba yin la /
NK083('u)001:1841: 'dir ni thams mkhas shing shes rab che ba'i gnad kyis /
NK083('u)001:1842: dngos rnams dbyer med du rtogs nas /
NK083('u)001:1843: 'dod pa'i dri ma dang pham pa'i nyes pa mi yong ba la /
NK083('u)001:1844: slar yon tan skye ba yin te /
NK083('u)001:1845: dug la sngags ma btab dang btab pa'i khyad par bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:1846: lnga pa rnam grangs su 'gyur tshul ni /
NK083('u)001:1847: gnyen po'i dbang gis brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs //
NK083('u)001:1849: spyir bslab pa gsum po de dug gsum gyi gnyen po yin la /
NK083('u)001:1850: bye brag tu nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong
NK083('u)001:1851: gi gnyen por chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi
NK083('u)001:1855: de'i gnyen por chos kyi don no //
NK083('u)001:1858: nyon mongs pa 'khrul snang 'di dag rgyu ma rig pa las byung ste /
NK083('u)001:1859: rig pa rang ngo ma shes la 'khrul snang rgyun sbrel nas chags sdang rmongs gsum skyes so //
NK083('u)001:1860: brgyad khri bzhi stong gi grangs ni /
NK083('u)001:1861: 'dod yon lnga la chags pa'i sems ni 'dod chags te /
NK083('u)001:1862: nang tshan nyi khri chig stong /
NK083('u)001:1863: rtsub 'gyur tsha ba dang bcas pa'i sems ni zhe sdang ste /
NK083('u)001:1864: nang tshan nyi khri chig stong /
NK083('u)001:1865: don mi rig mi go ba'i sems ni gti mug ste /
NK083('u)001:1866: nang tshan nyi khri chig stong /
NK083('u)001:1867: dug gsum gang gi yang phyogs gcig tu mi gnas
NK083('u)001:1868: la bag chags bag la nyal rkyen gang 'phrad du
NK083('u)001:1869: gsal bar ston pa ni dug gsum cha mnyam ste
NK083('u)001:1870: / nang tshan nyi khri chig stong ste /
NK083('u)001:1872: gnyis pa de'i don gnyen po ni /
NK083('u)001:1873: chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong ngo //
NK083('u)001:1875: rnam par dkar ba'i don ltung ba las 'dzin pas na chos /
NK083('u)001:1877: brgyad khri bzhi stong gi grangs ni /
NK083('u)001:1878: gang yang rung ba'i nyon mongs pa cig brtol skyes pa la /
NK083('u)001:1879: de'i gnyen por gyur tsam cig chos kyi sgo mo yin la /
NK083('u)001:1880: de 'dra ba brgyad khri bzhi stong ngo //
NK083('u)001:1881: de yang 'dod chags kyi gnyen por gyur tshad cig 'dul ba ste /
NK083('u)001:1882: nang tshan nyi khri chig stong ngo //
NK083('u)001:1883: zhe sdang gi gnyen por gyur tshad cig mdo sde ste /
NK083('u)001:1884: nang tshan nyi khri chig stong ngo //
NK083('u)001:1885: gti mug gi gnyen por gyur tshad cig mngon pa ste /
NK083('u)001:1886: nang tshan nyi khri chig stong ngo //
NK083('u)001:1887: cha mnyam gyi gnyen por gyur tshad cig gsang sngags te /
NK083('u)001:1888: nang tshan nyi khri chig stong ste /
NK083('u)001:1890: cha mnyam gyi gnyen por gsang sngags yin pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK083('u)001:1891: ma rig pa bag chags bag la nyal gyi gnyen
NK083('u)001:1892: po ni dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs rang byung
NK083('u)001:1893: lhan cig skyes pa yin la /
NK083('u)001:1894: de gsang sngags kyis ston pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1895: 'bras bu sangs rgyas sgrub pa la bslab pa gsum la gzhi bcas la /
NK083('u)001:1896: sdom pa gsum rgyud la skye dgos te /
NK083('u)001:1897: dper na ston thog sgrub pa la zhing sa dang so nam dgos pa bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:1898: des na de dag med kha med yin no //
NK083('u)001:1899: sems gsum sgo nas lam la 'jug pa ni //
NK083('u)001:1901: gnyis pa sems gsum gyis kha bsgyur ba la ni bzhi /
NK083('u)001:1905: de dag sde snod gsum du ngos bzung la bslab pa gsum du bstan pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1908: yid 'ong pha mar shes shing bde ldan bsgom //
NK083('u)001:1910: yul gang yang yid du 'ong zhing de dag bde
NK083('u)001:1911: ba dang ldan par bya'o snyam pa ni 'jig rten
NK083('u)001:1912: pa'i byams pa / yum sems can de dag la
NK083('u)001:1913: pha mar shes shing de rnams bde ba dang ldan
NK083('u)001:1914: par bya'o snyam du bsgom pa ni chos kyi byams
NK083('u)001:1915: pa'i byams pa / pa / de ltar sems can
NK083('u)001:1916: thams cad pha mar shes shing de dag la phan
NK083('u)001:1917: gdags pa'i blo skyes pa ni byams pa'i ting nge
NK083('u)001:1918: pa'i byams pa / pa / 'dzin / de rgyun
NK083('u)001:1919: chags su skyes pa ni byams pa tshad med pa'am
NK083('u)001:1922: sems can la dmigs pa'i byams pa ni /
NK083('u)001:1923: sems can thams cad pha mar shes shing de dag
NK083('u)001:1924: bde ba dang ldan par bya snyam pa'i blo skyes
NK083('u)001:1925: pa'o // chos la dmigs pa'i byams pa ni /
NK083('u)001:1926: don dam par cir yang ma grub pa yin yang kun rdzob rmi lam sgyu ma tsam gyi ngor /
NK083('u)001:1927: ma 'di rnams bde ba dang ldan par bya snyam pa'i blo'o //
NK083('u)001:1928: dmigs pa med pa'i byams pa ni /
NK083('u)001:1929: de ltar bsgoms pa'i dus nyid na /
NK083('u)001:1930: rang gzhan thams cad kyi ngo bo stong pa nyid spros bral nam mkha' ltar shes pas /
NK083('u)001:1931: gdangs ma 'gags par byams par dung nge /
NK083('u)001:1932: gshis ma grub par stong par lhag ge /
NK083('u)001:1933: ngo bo mi rtog mi dmigs shing 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1935: sems can pha ma sdug bsngal bsgral bar bsam //
NK083('u)001:1937: yul sems can thams cad sdug bsngal bar mthong nas sha tshas mi bzod pa'i snying rje skyes te /
NK083('u)001:1938: sdug bsngal de dag las bsgral bar 'dod pa ni 'jig rten pa'i snying rje /
NK083('u)001:1939: sems can thams cad pha mar shes nas de dag
NK083('u)001:1940: sdug bsngal du gnas pa la sha tshas mi bzod
NK083('u)001:1942: sdug bsngal las bsgral bar 'dod pa'i blo ni chos kyi snying rje /
NK083('u)001:1943: ma 'di rnams sdug bsngal ba la snying brtse bas
NK083('u)001:1944: sdug bsngal dang bral bar 'dod pa ni snying rje'i
NK083('u)001:1946: de dus rgyun chad med par skyes pa ni snying rje tshad med pa'am chen po zhes bya'o //
NK083('u)001:1948: sems can la dmigs pa'i snying rje ni /
NK083('u)001:1949: sems can duhkha dang bral bar bya snyam pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1950: chos la dmigs pa'i snying rje ni /
NK083('u)001:1951: don dam par cir yang ma grub pa yin yang
NK083('u)001:1952: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam gyi ngor dukha dang bral
NK083('u)001:1954: dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje ni /
NK083('u)001:1955: de ltar bsgom pa'i dus nyid na /
NK083('u)001:1956: rang gzhan thams cad kyi ngo bo stong pa nyid nam mkha' ltar shes pas /
NK083('u)001:1957: gdangs ma 'gags pa snying rjer dung nge //
NK083('u)001:1958: gshis ma grub pa stong pa nyid du lhag ge /
NK083('u)001:1959: ngo bo mi dmigs mi rtog cing 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1960: gsum pa byang chub kyi sems ni /
NK083('u)001:1961: sangs rgyas thob 'dod bsam pa len dang bsgrub //
NK083('u)001:1968: sems can thams cad kyi don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par 'dod pa smon pa'i sems so //
NK083('u)001:1969: de ltar khas blangs shing ma thob pa thob par byed pa smon pa'i sems bskyed /
NK083('u)001:1970: de'i mi mthun phyogs spong ba smon pa'i sdom pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1973: gzhan don du sangs rgyas thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK083('u)001:1974: de'i spyod pa sgrub par 'dod pa ni 'jug pa'i sems /
NK083('u)001:1975: de ltar khas blangs shing rgyud la sdom pa thob par byed pa 'jug pa'i sems bskyed /
NK083('u)001:1976: de'i spyod pa rgyun du bsgrub cing mi mthun phyogs spong ba ni 'jug pa'i sdom pa'o //
NK083('u)001:1978: sems can gyis sangs rgyas thob par 'dod pa'i bsam pa ni smon pa byang sems /
NK083('u)001:1979: de lag tu blangs nas sgrub pa ni 'jug pa byang sems /
NK083('u)001:1980: de nas smon pa gal che ste /
NK083('u)001:1981: smon pa byang sems la blo 'byongs na /
NK083('u)001:1983: smon pa ma skyes na 'jug pa bsgrub mi srid /
NK083('u)001:1984: de med na mi 'byung ba'i rgyu 'bras so //
NK083('u)001:1985: des na yang dag sangs rgyas thob pa la don dam sems bskyed dgos /
NK083('u)001:1986: don dam sems bskyed skye ba la kun rdzob byang sems dgos /
NK083('u)001:1988: snying rje skye ba la byams pa /
NK083('u)001:1989: byams pa sems can pha mar shes pa las skye'o //
NK083('u)001:1990: des na theg pa chen po'i lam gyi ngo bo ni /
NK083('u)001:1991: byams pa snying rje byang chub kyi sems yin pas med kha med yin no //
NK083('u)001:1992: de dag la brten nas rang gzhan gyi don thams
NK083('u)001:1993: cad 'grub pas lam gyi kha sgyur yin te rta'i
NK083('u)001:1994: kha lo srab kyis bsgyur ba bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:1995: bzhi pa de dag sde snod gsum du ngos bzung la bslab pa gsum du bstan pa ni /
NK083('u)001:1996: sems gsum sde gsum bslab gsum nyams gsum thugs //
NK083('u)001:1998: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad bdag
NK083('u)001:1999: gi pha ma yin cing drin bsam gyis mi khyab
NK083('u)001:2000: par yod pas / bde ba dang ldan par bya'o snyam du bsgom pa ni byams pa'i sems /
NK083('u)001:2001: ma 'di rnams duhkha sna tshogs la spyod pa snying re rje /
NK083('u)001:2002: duhkha de dag dang bral bar bya'o snyam du bsgom pa ni snying rje'i sems /
NK083('u)001:2003: ma 'di rnams bde ba dang ldan duhkha dang bral /
NK083('u)001:2004: myur du bla na med pa'i byang chub rin po
NK083('u)001:2005: che thob par bya'o snyam du bsgom pa ni byang
NK083('u)001:2007: de thams cad la kun tu snyoms shing rgyun chad med par bsgom mo //
NK083('u)001:2008: de la byams pa ni zhe sdang med pa'i sems /
NK083('u)001:2009: snying rje ni 'dod chags med pa'i sems /
NK083('u)001:2010: byang sems ni gti mug med pa'i sems so //
NK083('u)001:2011: de ka sde snod gsum yang yin te /
NK083('u)001:2014: byang sems mngon pa'i sde snod do //
NK083('u)001:2015: de ka bslab pa gsum yang yin te /
NK083('u)001:2016: 'dod chags med pa'i snying rje tshul khrims /
NK083('u)001:2017: zhe sdang med pa'i byams pa ting nge 'dzin /
NK083('u)001:2018: gti mug med pa'i byang sems de shes rab kyi bslab pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2019: de ka nyams gsum yang yin te /
NK083('u)001:2020: 'dod chags dang bral ba'i snying rje de bde ba'i nyams /
NK083('u)001:2021: zhe sdang dang bral ba'i byams pa de gsal ba'i nyams /
NK083('u)001:2022: gti mug dang bral ba'i byang sems de mi rtog pa'i nyams so //
NK083('u)001:2023: de ltar dug gsum gang yang med pa de sangs
NK083('u)001:2024: rgyas kyi thugs rnam par mi rtog pa yin pas
NK083('u)001:2028: byang sems gsum po de theg pa chen po'i lam gyi ngo bo yin pas med ka med do //
NK083('u)001:2029: khyad par gsang sngags lam gyi ngo bo ni //
NK083('u)001:2031: gnyis pa gsang sngags lam gyi ngo bo la lnga ste /
NK083('u)001:2032: rgyud smin par byed pa la dbang //
NK083('u)001:2033: smin pa grol bar byed pa la lta ba /
NK083('u)001:2034: lta ba goms par byed pa la sgom pa /
NK083('u)001:2035: de dang mi 'bral zhing rtsal sbyong ba la spyod pa /
NK083('u)001:2036: de dag las mi 'da' bar byed pa dam tshig go //
NK083('u)001:2039: bum gsang ye shes bde chen dbang bzhi bskur //
NK083('u)001:2043: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang /
NK083('u)001:2044: bde ba chen po'i dbang ngo //
NK083('u)001:2045: de bzhi'i don gtan la dbab pa la gnyis te /
NK083('u)001:2048: dang po go don bzhag pa /
NK083('u)001:2055: spang bya 'dod chags bzhi spong ba dang /
NK083('u)001:2056: sgrub byed phyag rgya bzhi ston pa dang /
NK083('u)001:2057: 'bras bu sku bzhi thob pa dang gsum du nges pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2060: 'dod khams kyi 'dod chags thams cad bzhir 'dus te /
NK083('u)001:2061: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed pa la dgod pas tshims pa'i chags pa yod pas /
NK083('u)001:2062: de dag par byed pa la bum dbang /
NK083('u)001:2063: 'phrul dga' ba la bltas pas tshims pa'i chags pa yod pas /
NK083('u)001:2064: de dag par byed pa la gsang dbang /
NK083('u)001:2065: dga' ldan pa la lag pa bcangs bas tshims pa'i chags pa yod pas /
NK083('u)001:2066: de dag par byed pa la shes rab ye shes /
NK083('u)001:2067: 'thab bral man chod la gnyis 'khyud kyis tshims pa'i chags pa yod pas /
NK083('u)001:2068: de dag par byed pa la bde ba chen po'o //
NK083('u)001:2071: bum dbang gis dam tshig phyag rgya /
NK083('u)001:2072: gsang dbang gis las kyi phyag rgya /
NK083('u)001:2073: shes rab ye shes kyis chos kyi phyag rgya /
NK083('u)001:2074: bde ba chen pos phyag rgya chen po ston pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2076: 'bras bu sku bzhi thob ga bum dbang gis sprul sku /
NK083('u)001:2078: shes rab ye shes kyis chos sku /
NK083('u)001:2079: bde chen gyis ngo bo nyid kyi sku thob pa dang bzhir nges so //
NK083('u)001:2080: gnyis pa go rim nges pa la gnyis te /
NK083('u)001:2081: lta ba la sbyar ba dang /
NK083('u)001:2082: rten dang brten pa'i tshul du sbyar ba'o //
NK083('u)001:2084: theg chen gyi lta ba thams cad bzhir 'dus te /
NK083('u)001:2089: de bzhin du dbang yang bzhir 'dus te /
NK083('u)001:2090: bum dbang gis snang ba rang sems sgyu ma ltar bstan pas /
NK083('u)001:2093: gsang dbang gis chos thams cad spros bral nam mkha' ltar bstan pas dbu ma'i lta ba /
NK083('u)001:2094: gsum pas bde stong dbyer med du bstan pas gsang sngags kyi lta ba /
NK083('u)001:2095: bzhi pa mtha' bral ye shes sangs rgyas su bstan pas rdzogs chen gyi lta ba'o //
NK083('u)001:2097: rten dang brten pa'i tshul du sbyar ba /
NK083('u)001:2100: de la khams byang sems brten /
NK083('u)001:2101: de la don dam byang sems brten pas /
NK083('u)001:2102: dang po lus 'dag pa la bum dbang /
NK083('u)001:2103: ngag rlung gi rang bzhin 'dag pa la gsang dbang /
NK083('u)001:2104: khams thig le byang sems 'dag pa la gsum pa /
NK083('u)001:2105: don dam byang sems rtogs par byed pa la bzhi pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2107: a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK083('u)001:2108: dri ma 'khrud pas na dbang ste /
NK083('u)001:2112: bzhi pas lus ngag yid gsum ka'i dri ma 'khrud pa ste /
NK083('u)001:2113: snod dag par bkrus nas bcud blugs su rung ba bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:2114: a b+hi she ka'i sgra las drangs na /
NK083('u)001:2115: skal ba 'jog pas na dbang ste /
NK083('u)001:2117: gnyis pas gtum mo tsan+da l+ai bsgom pa'i /
NK083('u)001:2118: gsum pas bde chen spros bral bsgom pa'i /
NK083('u)001:2119: bzhi pas zung 'jug blo 'das bsgom pa'i skal ba 'jogs pa ste /
NK083('u)001:2120: phas bu la phogs gtod pa bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:2121: a b+hi si ta'i sgra las drangs na /
NK083('u)001:2122: smin par byed pas na dbang ste /
NK083('u)001:2123: dang pos lus phung khams skye mched lha ru /
NK083('u)001:2124: gnyis pas ngag 'byung 'jug gnas gsum sngags su /
NK083('u)001:2125: gsum pas thig le bde chen ye shes /
NK083('u)001:2126: bzhi pas sems sangs rgyas chos sku ru smin par byed pas na dbang ste /
NK083('u)001:2127: rgyal por dbang bskur ba bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:2128: gnyis pa la ma nyams su blang tshul la bzhi ste /
NK083('u)001:2135: lus phung khams skye mched lha ru gnas pa bum dbang gi sa bon /
NK083('u)001:2136: ngag rlung dang yi ge sngags su gnas pa gsang dbang gi sa bon /
NK083('u)001:2137: khams dwangs ma kun d+ha bde chen du gnas pa gsum pa'i sa bon /
NK083('u)001:2138: sems sangs rgyas chos skur gnas pa bzhi pa'i sa bon yod pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2142: rtsa ba dbang bskur du btub pa yin pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2143: de'ang phyi rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas nang don gyi dkyil 'khor ston te /
NK083('u)001:2146: gsum pas thig le bde chen gyi //
NK083('u)001:2147: bzhi pas sems sku bzhi ngo bo nyid kyi dkyil 'khor du ston pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2148: gsum pa lam nyams su blang ba la mngon par rtogs pa bzhi ste /
NK083('u)001:2149: bskyed rim bum dbang gi mngon rtogs /
NK083('u)001:2150: rtsa rlung thig le gtum mo tsan d+ha l+ai thams cad gsang dbang gi mngon rtogs /
NK083('u)001:2151: rang gzhan gyi lus la brten nas 'og sgo bde
NK083('u)001:2152: chen sgom pa thams cad shes rab ye shes kyi
NK083('u)001:2153: mngon rtogs / de las skyes pa'i gnyis med ye
NK083('u)001:2154: shes chen po ni bde ba chen po'i mngon rtogs
NK083('u)001:2155: mngon rtogs / so // bzhi pa lam nyams su blangs pa'i 'bras bu bzhi ni /
NK083('u)001:2159: bzhi pas ngo bo nyid kyi sku thob pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2160: des na lus ngag rtsa khams thams cad sangs rgyas
NK083('u)001:2161: su ngo sprad pa dbang kho na yin pas med
NK083('u)001:2162: ka med do / gnyis pa smin pa grol bar byed pa'i /
NK083('u)001:2168: phyi nang snod bcud gzhal yas lha ru bskyed /
NK083('u)001:2177: snod bcud brtan g.yo'i dngos po thams cad gzhal yas khang dang lha'i rang bzhin du gnas pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2180: de ltar ngo ma shes pa snod bcud rang rgyud
NK083('u)001:2181: 'dzin pa kun btags glo bur gyi dri ma 'adi'o
NK083('u)001:2184: snod bcud thams cad gzhal yas khang dang lha ru bsgom pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2185: bzhi pa ni 'bras bu kun btags glo bur gyi dri ma dag nas /
NK083('u)001:2186: don rang mtshan mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2188: stong pa'i ngang las 'gags med kyi snying rje gnyis med yi ge'i rang bzhin las /
NK083('u)001:2190: bcud rang gzhan thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom /
NK083('u)001:2191: de la dam tshig ye shes gnyis las /
NK083('u)001:2192: rang gzhan gyi lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs su gnas pa ste /
NK083('u)001:2193: de las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig gi lhar gsal
NK083('u)001:2194: zhing tha mal gyi log rtog med pas na sems
NK083('u)001:2195: dapa'o // de ltar gdod nas gnas shing ye nas yod pa'i de nyid shes pa na ye shes /
NK083('u)001:2196: gnyis 'dzin gyi dri ma med pas na sems dpa' ste /
NK083('u)001:2197: dam tshig ye shes dbyer med pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2199: ye nas yod pa la ngo shes byas pa tsam las /
NK083('u)001:2200: rang bzhin gyi gnas nas spyan drangs la bstim zhes bya ba /
NK083('u)001:2201: yul can gzhan du grub pa ni med do //
NK083('u)001:2202: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la //
NK083('u)001:2204: de lta bu'i bskyed rim de la /
NK083('u)001:2205: lam du 'gro ba gnad gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:2206: tha mal gyi zhen pa sbyong ba la rnam pa gsal ba /
NK083('u)001:2207: de'i de nyid shes pa la rnam dag dran pa /
NK083('u)001:2208: kun btags mnyam rjes med pa la nga rgyal brtan pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2210: tha mal gyi zhen pa sbyong ba /
NK083('u)001:2211: rnam pa gsal bar bsgoms pas thun mong gi yon tan thams cad 'byung ste /
NK083('u)001:2212: gdan che la brtan pas tshe ring ba /
NK083('u)001:2213: zhabs bgrad kham che bas sdod tshugs pa /
NK083('u)001:2214: sku lang tsho rgyas shing yid du 'ong ba bsgoms pas nad nyung khams bzang ba /
NK083('u)001:2215: phyag mtshan gsal bas bsam pa 'grub pa /
NK083('u)001:2216: rgyan tshang bas 'byor pa ldan pa /
NK083('u)001:2217: zhal dang mche ba sku mdog gsal bar bsgoms pas
NK083('u)001:2218: thams cad bka' nyan cing snang ba dbang du 'dus
NK083('u)001:2220: des na gtso 'khor sku mdog zhal phyag thams cad
NK083('u)001:2221: ma lus shing gsal bar bsgoms pas bar chad gang
NK083('u)001:2222: gis kyang mi tshugs shing thun mong gi yon tan
NK083('u)001:2224: gsal ba gang yang med na /
NK083('u)001:2225: yon tan gang yang mi 'byung ngo //
NK083('u)001:2226: gnyis pa rnam dag dran pa la gnyis te /
NK083('u)001:2230: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi la sogs par bsgom pa na /
NK083('u)001:2237: dkar po skyon gyis ma gos pas /
NK083('u)001:2238: ser po yon tan rgyas pa /
NK083('u)001:2239: dmar po thugs rje chags pa /
NK083('u)001:2240: ljang gu phrin las thogs med /
NK083('u)001:2241: mthing ga'am nag po chos nyid mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK083('u)001:2245: rin po che yon tan 'byung ba /
NK083('u)001:2246: pad+ma skyon gyis ma gos pa /
NK083('u)001:2247: rgya gram mam ral gri ni phrin las thogs pa med pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2248: de bzhin du rang rang gi sgrub thabs gang yin pa'i gzhung bzhin byas pas yon tan 'byung ngo //
NK083('u)001:2249: gnyis pa don gyi rnam dag ni /
NK083('u)001:2250: de dag kyang bden dngos su grub pa med pas /
NK083('u)001:2251: rang bzhin stong pa nyid du shes par bya'o //
NK083('u)001:2253: gdangs ma 'agagagasa pa lha ru lam me /
NK083('u)001:2254: gshis ma grub pa stong par chom me /
NK083('u)001:2255: ngo bo gsal stong gnyis med du lhang nge /
NK083('u)001:2256: de ltar gnyis med du bsgoms pas tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:2257: gsum pa nga rgyal brtan pa ni /
NK083('u)001:2258: gsal rung mi gsal rung lha rang yin no snyam pa'i bsam pa bya zhing /
NK083('u)001:2259: tha mal gyi snang ba med par bya'o //
NK083('u)001:2260: des na mchog thun mong gi yon tan thams cad
NK083('u)001:2261: tshe 'di nyid las 'byung ba ni bskyed pa'i rim
NK083('u)001:2262: pa yin pas med ka med yin no //
NK083('u)001:2263: bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi don ni /
NK083('u)001:2264: kun rdzob lam du byed pa bskyed rim /
NK083('u)001:2265: don dam mngon du byed pa la rdzogs rim /
NK083('u)001:2266: de gnyis tha dad gnyis su med pas bskyed rdzogs dbyer med zung 'jug yin no //
NK083('u)001:2267: de yang snod bcud thams cad gdangs ma 'gags par gsal ba ni gzugs sku /
NK083('u)001:2268: gshis stong par gnas pa ni chos sku /
NK083('u)001:2269: ngo bo cir yang mi rtog pa ni gnyis med yin te /
NK083('u)001:2270: gdangs gzugs sku yin tsam na /
NK083('u)001:2272: gshis chos skur gnas pa las /
NK083('u)001:2274: de'i gnad phyis dbyer med las 'das pa med do //
NK083('u)001:2276: skye 'gags gnyis med rang byung mtha' las 'das //
NK083('u)001:2278: gzhi stong pa'i gnas lugs sems nyid kyi bzhugs tshul /
NK083('u)001:2279: shes bya'i gshis des dngos por ma skyes /
NK083('u)001:2281: tha dad du ma grub pa'i skye 'gag gnyis med do //
NK083('u)001:2283: dngos por ma skyes pas stong pa /
NK083('u)001:2284: dngos med du ma 'gags pas rig pa /
NK083('u)001:2285: tha dad du ma grub pas gnyis med do //
NK083('u)001:2286: des na chos thams cad rang gi sems yin la /
NK083('u)001:2287: sems ni stong pa nyid do //
NK083('u)001:2295: rang stong pas yul med pa ste rtag pa'i chos su mi sdod pa /
NK083('u)001:2296: ye stong pas dus glo bur du byung ba ma yin te gdod ma nas stong pa /
