NK083('u)001:2297: rang bzhin gyis stong pas sus kyang byas pa ma yin te gshis rang stong pa /
NK083('u)001:2298: kun stong pas nyi tshe'i stong pa ma yin te chos thams cad kyi chos nyid /
NK083('u)001:2299: mnyam par stong pas ro gcig ste bzang ngan med pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2300: mdor na chos thams cad kyi chos nyid gshis cir yang ma grub pa nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK083('u)001:2301: stong pa de nyid kyi gdangs 'gags med du 'char bas na /
NK083('u)001:2304: snang tshad gcig rang snang bas gzhan ma yin pa /
NK083('u)001:2305: bkag pa med pas zang thal du snang ba /
NK083('u)001:2306: gtad so med pas kha yan du snang ba /
NK083('u)001:2307: dus btab med pas nges med du snang ba /
NK083('u)001:2308: phyogs gcig tu ma grub pa sna tshogs su snang ba ste /
NK083('u)001:2309: 'bras bu sangs rgyas pa'i dus na sku dang ye shes yon tan sna tshogs su snang /
NK083('u)001:2310: lam rnal 'byor pa'i dus na nyams dang ting nge 'dzin rtogs pa'i bye brag sna tshogs su snang /
NK083('u)001:2311: rgyu sems can gyi dus na rigs drug gi snang
NK083('u)001:2312: ba thams cad bde sdug skyon yon sna tshogs su
NK083('u)001:2313: snang ngo // mdor na gshis can yang ma yin
NK083('u)001:2314: pa'i gnad kas gdangs cir yang 'char ba nam mkha'i
NK083('u)001:2316: des na stong pa'i gdangs 'gags med du snang la /
NK083('u)001:2317: snang ba'i rang bzhin stong par gnas pas snang stong gnyis med /
NK083('u)001:2318: de yang snang ba'i steng du stong pa spyan drangs pa'am /
NK083('u)001:2319: stong pa snang ba'i lha la btab pa'i gnyis med ma yin te /
NK083('u)001:2320: snang ba'i rang bzhin dbyings stong pa nyid du lhang nge /
NK083('u)001:2321: dbyings stong pa'i gdangs de ka rig pa 'gags med kyi rol pa khra shig ge /
NK083('u)001:2322: stong pa dbyings kyi chos nyid /
NK083('u)001:2323: gsal ba ye shes kyi pho sgo /
NK083('u)001:2324: gnyis med gshis kyi gnas lugs so //
NK083('u)001:2325: yang skye med gags med kyi steng du bkug pa'am /
NK083('u)001:2326: 'gags med skye med kyi zla la btab pa lta bu ni ma yin te /
NK083('u)001:2327: skye 'gags gnyis med sku gsum du grong nge /
NK083('u)001:2328: mdor na gnyis bsdus thams cad gnyis med gnyug ma chos sku'o //
NK083('u)001:2329: de yang chu dang 'o ma ltar 'dres pa'am /
NK083('u)001:2330: phye chu ltar bsres pa'i gnyis med min /
NK083('u)001:2333: shes nas gnyis med du song ba ma yin /
NK083('u)001:2336: bzang ngan med pas gnyis med kyang min te /
NK083('u)001:2337: chos thams cad kyi gshis sam /
NK083('u)001:2339: gnas lugs de gnyis med thig le nyag gcig tu gnas pas /
NK083('u)001:2343: so so ma yin tha mi dad dbyer med pa ste /
NK083('u)001:2344: gnyis ma grub pas gnyis med do //
NK083('u)001:2345: thog de ru song ba la gnyis med rtogs zhes bya'o //
NK083('u)001:2347: gshis thog tu song ba zhes bya'o //
NK083('u)001:2348: mdor na gshis cir yang ma grub /
NK083('u)001:2350: ngo bo cir yang mi rtog /mtshan nyid mtha' dang bral /
NK083('u)001:2351: don thig le nyag gcig /cir yang ma yin pas cir yang 'char ba la /
NK083('u)001:2352: cir yang 'char bas cir yang ma yin pa ste /
NK083('u)001:2353: nam mkha' dang cho 'phrul dbyer med pa bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:2355: stong pa dang snang ba 'bral ma myong /
NK083('u)001:2356: snang ba dang stong pa 'bral ma myong /
NK083('u)001:2357: snang bas stong pa ma spangs /
NK083('u)001:2358: stong pas snang ba ma spangs pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2359: de yang rang snang ngo shes pas snang ba sems su thag chod pa /
NK083('u)001:2360: med 'dzin chad pa las grol ba'i lta ba /
NK083('u)001:2361: kun rdzob shes pa'i shes rab /
NK083('u)001:2362: rang stong rang ngo shes te sems nyid stong par thag chod pa /
NK083('u)001:2363: yod 'dzin rtag pa las grol ba'i lta ba /
NK083('u)001:2364: don dam shes pa'i shes rab /
NK083('u)001:2365: zung 'jug rang ngo shes te snang stong gnyis med du thag chod pas /
NK083('u)001:2366: rtag chad gnyis las grol ba'i lta ba /
NK083('u)001:2367: tha mi dad shes pa'i shes rab bo //
NK083('u)001:2368: de la rgyu dang rkyen med sus kyang ma byas pas na rang byung /
NK083('u)001:2369: phyogs gcig tu mi gnas pas mtha' las 'das pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2370: de ni skye med kyi ngos nas cir yang ma yin te /
NK083('u)001:2371: yin pa med pa'i lta ba /
NK083('u)001:2372: 'gags med kyi ngos nas gang yang yin pas /
NK083('u)001:2373: min pa med pa'i lta ba /
NK083('u)001:2375: yin min yod med rtag chad kyi mtha' las 'das pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2377: bshad pa mtha' las 'das par bshad /
NK083('u)001:2378: sgom pa mtha' las 'das pa bsgom /
NK083('u)001:2379: spyod pa mtha' las 'das pa spyod /
NK083('u)001:2380: bsngo ba mtha' las 'das par bsngo /
NK083('u)001:2383: skyon ye dag /yon tan ye rdzogs /
NK083('u)001:2384: gnyis ma grub pas gnyis med /
NK083('u)001:2385: zung ma rnyed pas zung 'jug /mtha' ma rnyed pas mtha' bral /
NK083('u)001:2386: bzang ngan med pas kun tu bzang po /
NK083('u)001:2387: sdig pa ma rnyed pas dge sdig med /
NK083('u)001:2391: gnad gsum bcun pas rtog med rang gsal 'char //
NK083('u)001:2395: skyes pa rang gi ngo bo /
NK083('u)001:2402: bzhag thabs sems kyi gnad do //
NK083('u)001:2404: gnas dben par mal bde ba stan 'bol ba'i steng du /
NK083('u)001:2407: lag pa mnyam bzhag /lus po ya yo dang sgye sgur med par rang so la cham bzhag go //
NK083('u)001:2408: des sgom rang babs su yong la /
NK083('u)001:2409: 'phrul 'khor bca' ma shes na sgom mi skye'o //
NK083('u)001:2410: gnyis pa lta stangs mig gi gnad gsum ni /
NK083('u)001:2413: logs dang zur du mi gcu bar thad ka'i so gcig la phur tshugs su gtad do //
NK083('u)001:2414: des sgom rang babs su 'ong ste /
NK083('u)001:2415: mig dang shes pa gnad gcig yin no //
NK083('u)001:2416: lta stangs med na sgom mi 'char ro //
NK083('u)001:2417: gsum pa bzhag thabs sems kyi gnad gsum ni /
NK083('u)001:2418: de tha mal du ma yengs /
NK083('u)001:2420: yid kyis bzo ma byas par shes pa rang lugs su cham bzhag go //
NK083('u)001:2421: des sgom rang babs su 'ong la /
NK083('u)001:2422: yengs pa dang 'gyus na sgom mi skye'o //
NK083('u)001:2423: gnyis pa skyes pa rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK083('u)001:2424: de ltar rang lugs su bzhag pas rnam rtog phra rags thams cad rang sar nyal zhi nas /
NK083('u)001:2425: sems rang sar lhag ge gnas pa zhig 'ong //
NK083('u)001:2426: de ka la zhi gnas zer /
NK083('u)001:2427: de'i gdangs ma 'gags par yul med rang gsal du rjen ne lhang nge ba zhig 'ong /
NK083('u)001:2429: de gnyis shes pa skad cig ma'i steng na dbyer
NK083('u)001:2430: med gcig gi ngo bor hril gnas pa zhig yong
NK083('u)001:2431: / de ka la zhi gnas lhag mthong gnyis med zer ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:2432: de blo yul du byas na go ba /
NK083('u)001:2433: yul med du nyams su myong na nyams /
NK083('u)001:2434: shes pa nyid de'i ngo bor hril le 'dug na rtogs pa yin /
NK083('u)001:2435: dus gsum sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa bya ba de yin /
NK083('u)001:2436: de bla ma gdams ngag che nas byas pa min /
NK083('u)001:2437: slob ma shes rab che nas byung ba min /
NK083('u)001:2438: gnas lugs sam gshis thog tu phebs pa bya ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:2440: de ltar bsgoms pas bde gas la mi rtog pa'i nyams su 'char te /
NK083('u)001:2441: rnam par rtog pa dang bral ba'i shes pa la mi rtog pa zhes bya'o //
NK083('u)001:2443: bsgom bya sgom byed kyi zhen snang med pas bzang rtog dang bral /
NK083('u)001:2444: rnam rtog phra rags kyi rgyun chad nas ngan rtog dang bral /
NK083('u)001:2445: rig pa yul med du rang ngo shes pas lung ma bstan dang bral ba'o //
NK083('u)001:2446: rtog med kyi ngang nas rig pa'i gdangs ma 'a gags par ye re 'dug pa ni gsal ba'o //
NK083('u)001:2448: yul med de rang gsal ba /
NK083('u)001:2449: glo bur du byung ba ma yin te ye nas gsal ba /
NK083('u)001:2450: sus kyang ma byas te rang bzhin gyis gsal ba'o //
NK083('u)001:2451: de la mi mthun pa'i 'gal rkyen med pas bde ba'o //
NK083('u)001:2453: mtshan ma'i zug rngu med de mtshan ma med pa'i bde ba /
NK083('u)001:2454: gnyis 'dzin gyi zhen snang med pas gnyis su med pa'i bde ba /
NK083('u)001:2455: de la rgyu rkyen med pas 'dus ma byas kyi bde ba'o //
NK083('u)001:2456: de lta bu'i nyams skyes pa la ma chags pa gsum sgom pa skyon med yin te /
NK083('u)001:2457: bde ba la ma chags pa smyon pa lta bu'i spyod pa /
NK083('u)001:2458: gsal ba la ma chags pa bu chung gi rmi lam lta bu /
NK083('u)001:2459: mi rtog pa la ma chags pa brtul zhugs mthar phyin pa'i rnal 'byor ba lta bu'o //
NK083('u)001:2460: de la chags na srid pa gsum du gol te /
NK083('u)001:2461: bde ba la chags na 'dod khams su /
NK083('u)001:2462: gsal ba la chags na gzugs khams su /
NK083('u)001:2463: mi rtog pa la chags na gzugs med du gol /
NK083('u)001:2464: de dag la ma chags snyam yang chags sems phra mo 'ong zhing /
NK083('u)001:2465: ma zhen ma mno yang zhen chos phra mo yod pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2466: bzhi pa gol sa bcad cing skyon bsal ba la /
NK083('u)001:2467: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dagu'o //
NK083('u)001:2468: de yang 'dod khams kyi rnam rtog spong ba la /
NK083('u)001:2469: bsam gtan gyi snyoms 'jug bzhi ste /
NK083('u)001:2470: gzung 'dzin gyi rnam rtog med pa las bsgom bya
NK083('u)001:2471: sgom byed kyi dpyod pa dang bcas pa ni bsam
NK083('u)001:2472: gtan dang po'o // rtog pa dang dpyod pa med
NK083('u)001:2473: la dga' ba'i ting 'dzin gyi ro myong ba'i 'dzin
NK083('u)001:2474: pa dang bcas pa ni bsam gtan gnyis pa /
NK083('u)001:2475: sems g.yo ba med la dbugs dbyung rngub dang bcas pa ni gsum pa /
NK083('u)001:2476: rnam rtog thams cad dang bral ba'i gsal stong go ma 'gags pa ni bsam gtan bzhi pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2477: gzugs khams kyi rnam rtog spong ba la /
NK083('u)001:2478: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa bzhi ste /
NK083('u)001:2479: chos thams cad nam mkha' lta bu yin no snyam
NK083('u)001:2480: du blos brtags nas de la mnyam par 'jog pa
NK083('u)001:2482: rnam par shes pa mtha' yas shing phyogs med yin
NK083('u)001:2483: no snyam du blos brtags nas de la mnyam par
NK083('u)001:2484: 'jog pa ni rnam shes mtha' yas /
NK083('u)001:2485: 'du shes kyi gsal rig yod pa'ang ma yin te /
NK083('u)001:2487: blos byar ma btub pa yin no snyam du blos
NK083('u)001:2488: brtags nas de la mnyam par 'jog pa ni yod
NK083('u)001:2489: min med min / sems ni ci'i ngo bor ma
NK083('u)001:2490: grub ste med cing stong pa yin no snyam du
NK083('u)001:2491: blos brtags nas de la blo 'jog pa ni cir
NK083('u)001:2492: yang ma grub pa'i skye mched do //
NK083('u)001:2493: de dag blos brtags pa dang /
NK083('u)001:2495: sems kyi nyon mongs pa'i dri ma bag tsam yod pa /
NK083('u)001:2496: thams cad mi rtog pa la gnas pa 'gog pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa ste /
NK083('u)001:2497: tshogs drug yul la 'jug pa nang du 'gag cing /
NK083('u)001:2498: rlung sems kyi 'gyu ba rgyun chad pa la ji
NK083('u)001:2499: srid du mnyam par bzhag gi bar la gnas pa
NK083('u)001:2500: ste zhi gnas gyi ting nge 'dzin mthar thug pa
NK083('u)001:2501: yin la / de shes rab kyis gsos btab nas mnyam par 'jog pa ni /
NK083('u)001:2502: so sor brtag 'gog /gshis kyis gzhol phyogs der song ba ni brtag min gyis 'gog pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2503: de ni don dam pa'i lung ma bstan te /
NK083('u)001:2504: de ltar snyoms 'jug dgu po de la bsam gtan gyi snyoms 'jug bzhi ni /
NK083('u)001:2505: lhag mthong skyed par byed pa zhi gnas te /
NK083('u)001:2506: bsam gtan bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK083('u)001:2507: gshis dang mthun zhing 'jig rten pa'i ting nge 'dzin rnams kyi nang nas mchog go //
NK083('u)001:2508: gzugs med pa'i snyoms 'jug bzhi ni /
NK083('u)001:2509: ting nge 'dzin gyi gol sa yin no //
NK083('u)001:2511: nyan thos bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK083('u)001:2512: de ltar de rnams ngo shes pas /
NK083('u)001:2513: ting nge 'dzin gyi bye brag phyed cing /
NK083('u)001:2514: rang gi sgom pa de la /
NK083('u)001:2515: de dag gi sel dang gol sa mi 'byung ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:2516: de ltar gol sa re dogs bcad nas /
NK083('u)001:2517: sgom skyon med du nyams su blangs pas /
NK083('u)001:2518: mnyam bzhag la de ltar bde gsal mi rtog pa gsum du seng nge ye re gnas /
NK083('u)001:2519: rjes thob la snang ba bkra gsal /
NK083('u)001:2520: rmi lam sgyu ma lta bu bun long 'char /
NK083('u)001:2522: bsod nams kyi bre kha khengs /
NK083('u)001:2523: ting nge 'dzin gyi drod thob ste /
NK083('u)001:2524: des tshogs lam mthar phyin mos spyod kyi sa la slebs pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:2525: de yun ring du bsgoms pas rang gis rang la
NK083('u)001:2526: yod pa'i don yul med rang gsal mngon sum du
NK083('u)001:2527: mthong zhing rang ngo shes pa ni mthong lam ste
NK083('u)001:2528: / snang rig stong gsum yul med du gsal /
NK083('u)001:2529: chos nyid zag pa med pa'i don mngon sum du mthong /
NK083('u)001:2530: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa rtsa ba nas zad /
NK083('u)001:2531: rgyu 'bras rang rgyud stong par rtogs te /
NK083('u)001:2533: dang po rab tu dga' ba'i sa ste /
NK083('u)001:2534: mnyam bzhag sangs rgyas su mtshungs pa /
NK083('u)001:2535: rjes thob sgyu ma lta bur 'char ro //
NK083('u)001:2536: de goms shing brtan par bskyangs pas /
NK083('u)001:2537: gnyis chos thams cad gnyis med du song /
NK083('u)001:2538: rang snang rang ngo shes pas snang sems gcig tu 'dres /
NK083('u)001:2539: stong pa rgyu 'bras su shar bas rten 'brel mngon du gyur te /
NK083('u)001:2540: mnyam bzhag la chos thams cad yul med rig pa'i ngo bor gsal /
NK083('u)001:2541: rjes thob la snang yul bag tsam yod pa ni sgom lam mo //
NK083('u)001:2542: de rgyun bsrings pas 'khor 'das thams cad las /
NK083('u)001:2545: yul med rang gsal mngon du gyur pas /
NK083('u)001:2546: shes sgrib gtan nas med de /
NK083('u)001:2547: thams cad ye shes su shar ba'i skad cig ma
NK083('u)001:2548: de mthar phyin gyi lam ste sangs rgyas kyi sa'o
NK083('u)001:2549: // bzhi pa spyod pa bstan pa ni /
NK083('u)001:2550: so spyi bogs gsang yang dag kho na spyod //
NK083('u)001:2553: dang po lam gyi so zugs pa la thun mong spyi'i spyod pa /
NK083('u)001:2554: bar du de la bogs 'don pa la brtul zhugs gsang ba'i spyod pa /
NK083('u)001:2555: tha ma yang dag de kho na nyid mthar phyin pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2558: mi tshe thams cad rjes la skyel zhing /
NK083('u)001:2559: rjes ni spyod pa kho na yin pas /
NK083('u)001:2560: spyod pa ni gal shin tu che ste /
NK083('u)001:2561: lta ba mthon po blo yul du go yang /
NK083('u)001:2562: spyod pa don dang mi mthun na lam log /sgom
NK083('u)001:2563: pa bzang po skyes kyang rjes spyod de bzhin ma
NK083('u)001:2565: des rgyu 'bras kyi gnad go bar bya ste dkar
NK083('u)001:2566: nag gi las shin tu phra ba nas 'dor len
NK083('u)001:2567: bya / de ni yang dag pa'i lam /
NK083('u)001:2568: shes bya'i de kho na nyid /
NK083('u)001:2569: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i ngo bo yin te /
NK083('u)001:2570: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ste //
NK083('u)001:2571: dge ba phun sum tshogs par spyad //
NK083('u)001:2572: rang gi sems ni yongs su 'dul //
NK083('u)001:2573: 'di ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin /
NK083('u)001:2575: des na mi lus thob nas dam pa'i chos tshul bzhin du byed na /
NK083('u)001:2576: lus ngag yid gsum tha mal du skad cig kyang 'chor thabs med pas /
NK083('u)001:2577: nyin mo shes pa bzo med tshogs drug lhug pa rmi lam sgyu ma lta bur nyams su blang /
NK083('u)001:2578: nub mo shes pa spro bsdu med par blo rtog
NK083('u)001:2579: med kyi ngang la gnyid dang chos nyid bsres la
NK083('u)001:2580: nyal / rmi lam gyi 'khrul snang yang dag pa'i lam du sbyangs /
NK083('u)001:2581: de yang byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems sam /
NK083('u)001:2582: bskyed rdzogs la sogs pa gang la goms par sbyang ngo //
NK083('u)001:2583: nang nub thun gtor dang rgyun gtor ma chag pa btang /
NK083('u)001:2584: bdun rnam dag bya zhing phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul /
NK083('u)001:2585: yi ge brgya bas sdig pa bshags /
NK083('u)001:2590: byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems sbyang /
NK083('u)001:2591: bskyed pa'i rim pa snang srid lha'i dkyil 'khor bsgom /
NK083('u)001:2592: rdzogs pa'i rim pa snang la rang bzhin med pa
NK083('u)001:2593: chu nang gi zla ba lta bu gnyis med chen
NK083('u)001:2594: po'i ngang la bzhag /mjug dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo
NK083('u)001:2595: / de ltar byed pa po theg pa spyi dang tshul mthun /
NK083('u)001:2596: yang dag pa'i lam du 'gro ste lam gyi so tshugs 'gro ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:2597: gnyis pa bar du brtul zhugs gsang ba'i spyod pa bstan pa ni /
NK083('u)001:2598: gong ltar byas te lam gyi so tshugs /
NK083('u)001:2600: yin lugs lta ba'i gding bag tsam rnyed pa dang /
NK083('u)001:2601: lam de nyid la bogs 'don cing /
NK083('u)001:2602: rtogs pa dras thag bcad pa'i phyir gsang spyod nyams su blang ngo //
NK083('u)001:2603: de yang rang bsgom pa gal che zhing /
NK083('u)001:2604: nyams len brtan pa gcig gi sgo nas bcad cing nyams su blang ngo //
NK083('u)001:2605: theg pa chen po'i nyams len tshul bzhir 'dus te /
NK083('u)001:2607: byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems la blo sbyangs pa dang /
NK083('u)001:2608: yul thams cad brdzun par shes pa'i lta ba'o //
NK083('u)001:2610: bskyed pa'i rim pa lha'i 'khor lo dang /
NK083('u)001:2611: rdzogs pa'i rim pa gnyis med mtha' bral gyi lta ba'o //
NK083('u)001:2613: byang chub kyi sems sbyang ba /
NK083('u)001:2614: rang byang chub kyi sems la blo 'byongs nas sems
NK083('u)001:2615: can thams cad pha mar shes na des bcad de
NK083('u)001:2617: bdag 'dzin gyi ltos thag bcad cing byang sems kyi shugs phyin pa'i phyir gnyan sar phyin te /
NK083('u)001:2618: de yang sa dmigs sam gang 'jigs 'jigs 'dra ba gcig tu mal bcas la /
NK083('u)001:2619: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs 'gro bya /
NK083('u)001:2620: bla ma la gsol ba gdab /
NK083('u)001:2621: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed /
NK083('u)001:2622: de nas gnas bdag de nyid kyis gtsor byas pa'i
NK083('u)001:2623: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad la
NK083('u)001:2624: byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems tshad med pa
NK083('u)001:2625: dung dung ba yun ring du bsgom /
NK083('u)001:2626: de nas don dam byang sems kyi sems la lha 'dre gnyis med spros bral bde ba chen po /
NK083('u)001:2627: skye 'gags gnas gsum dang bral ba'i ngang la nyal la bsdad /
NK083('u)001:2628: de la 'jigs pa dang nyam nga ba la sogs pa rnam rtog byung na /
NK083('u)001:2629: shes pa khrims sgrim chun bcun la /
NK083('u)001:2631: sems can pha mar ma shes par 'drer 'dzin gyi
NK083('u)001:2632: rnam rtog skyes te de'i rang gzugs shar ba yin
NK083('u)001:2633: pas / khyod kyi sngar gyi byang chub sems de
NK083('u)001:2634: ni kha tshig dang go yul las mi 'dug pas
NK083('u)001:2635: pas / / des don mi 'grub snyam du chun
NK083('u)001:2636: gcun te byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems dung
NK083('u)001:2637: pas / / pa bsgom la / gzhi bdag des
NK083('u)001:2638: gtsor byas pa'i lha 'dre thams cad la lus ltos
NK083('u)001:2639: med kyi sbyin pa ling btang la /
NK083('u)001:2640: sha khrag lhag rkang ji ltar dga' ba ltar khyer snyams pa blos ling btang la /
NK083('u)001:2641: byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems la lhan bzhag go //
NK083('u)001:2642: de bzhin du 'drer 'dzin dang lha 'dre'i rnam rtog
NK083('u)001:2643: byung ma thag /rang gi byang chub sems la ltems
NK083('u)001:2644: rkyang byung nas / 'drer 'dzin gyi rnam rtog skyes pa'i rang gzugs yin snyam du bsams shing /
NK083('u)001:2645: lus ltos med kyi sbyin pa /
NK083('u)001:2646: sems byams snying rje la lhan lhan bzhag go //
NK083('u)001:2647: mngon sum la sogs par byung na /
NK083('u)001:2648: de nyid kyi 'phang du mchongs shing /
NK083('u)001:2649: kha nang du phyin te lus ltos med kyi sbyin pa btang /
NK083('u)001:2650: sems byams snying rje dang mi 'bral bar bya /
NK083('u)001:2651: mjug smon lam gdab cing dge ba'i rtsa ba yongs su bsngo'o //
NK083('u)001:2652: de nas rang gi 'drer 'dzin gyi rnam rtog rgyun nam chad tsa na /
NK083('u)001:2653: rnam rtog choms dang 'dre thul ba dus gcig 'ong /
NK083('u)001:2654: 'drer snang dang cho 'phrul zhi nas gnas bdag de nyid rang gi dbang du gyur te /
NK083('u)001:2655: dgra thul ba dang gnangs lon pa dus gcig 'ong ngo //
NK083('u)001:2656: sems can pha mar shes pas 'drer 'dzin gyi rtog pa mi skye /
NK083('u)001:2657: de skyes na pha mar ma shes pas da rung pha ma'i blo sbyang /
NK083('u)001:2659: yul thams cad rdzun par shes shing /
NK083('u)001:2660: snang tshad rmi lam sgyu mar shes nas /
NK083('u)001:2663: snang ba bden dngos su 'dzin pa'i zhen snang bcad cing /
NK083('u)001:2664: rdzun snang gi lta ba la bogs dbyung ba'i phyir /
NK083('u)001:2665: gang gnyan pa'i sar phyin la /
NK083('u)001:2669: kun rdzob tu yul thams cad rdzun pa /
NK083('u)001:2672: rmi lam sgyu ma lta bur shes pa'i ngang nas /
NK083('u)001:2673: don dam par cir yang ma grub pa spros bral stong pa'i ngang la nyal te bsdad do //
NK083('u)001:2677: bag tsha ba la sogs pa byung na /
NK083('u)001:2680: yul thams cad ni brdzun zhing /
NK083('u)001:2682: snang ba 'di rmi lam sgyu ma lta bur ma shes par /
NK083('u)001:2684: de'i rang gzugs shar ba yin pas /
NK083('u)001:2685: khyod kyi bden med kyi lta ba de ni /
NK083('u)001:2686: kha tshig don spyi blo yul /
NK083('u)001:2687: go ba tsam las mi 'dug pas /
NK083('u)001:2688: 'dis yang dag pa'i don mi 'grub snyam du shes pa chun gcun te grungs bton la /
NK083('u)001:2689: bden med sgyu ma lta bu'i ngang du ling bzhag go //
NK083('u)001:2690: de bzhin du 'drer 'dzin gyi rnam rtog dang /
NK083('u)001:2691: cho 'phrul la sogs pa byung ma thag tu /
NK083('u)001:2692: bden med kyi don ma shes par 'drer 'dzin gyi
NK083('u)001:2693: rnam rtog skyes pa'i rang gzugs shar ba yin snyam
NK083('u)001:2694: du bsam gyin / bden med sgyu ma lta bur la ngos tsir tsir bzung ngo //
NK083('u)001:2695: mngon sum la sogs pa byung na /
NK083('u)001:2696: bden med kyi don shes par byas la /
NK083('u)001:2697: de nyid kyi 'phang du phyin pas med snang du zang thal 'agro'o //
NK083('u)001:2698: de nas yul thams cad brdzun par shes shing /
NK083('u)001:2699: rang gi 'drer 'dzin gyi rnam rtog rgyun nam chad tsam na /
NK083('u)001:2701: rtog pa sangs pa dang 'dre zad pa dus gcig 'ong /
NK083('u)001:2703: gsum pa rang la bskyed rim brtan po yod cing snang ba lha skur 'char na /
NK083('u)001:2706: snod bcud lha ru 'dzin pa'i zhen snang bcad cing /
NK083('u)001:2707: bskyed rim la bogs dbyung ba'i phyir /
NK083('u)001:2712: de nas gnas de gzhal yas khang du bsgom /
NK083('u)001:2713: gzhi bdag des gtsor byas pa'i sems can thams cad yi dam lha ru bsgom /
NK083('u)001:2717: de ltar yun ring du bsgom /
NK083('u)001:2718: de nas don dam stong nyid gnad kyis zin par bya ste /
NK083('u)001:2719: snang la rang bzhin med pa'i ngang la nyal lo //
NK083('u)001:2720: der nyam nga ba dang khu 'phrig gi rnam rtog byung na /
NK083('u)001:2721: shes pa rtse gcig tu hril btang la /
NK083('u)001:2723: snang ba yi dam du ma shes par 'dre gdon du 'dzin pa'i rtog pa skyes yod pas /
NK083('u)001:2724: de'i rang gzugs shar ba yin /
NK083('u)001:2725: khyod kyi bskyed rim de tshig dang go ba blo
NK083('u)001:2726: yul las mi 'dug /des sangs gang du rgya snyam
NK083('u)001:2727: du bsam ste / shes pa phyogs gcig tu hril btang la /
NK083('u)001:2728: rang gzhan thams cad yi dam lha ru lam bsgom ste /
NK083('u)001:2729: rang gi tha mal gyi lus 'di bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs la /
NK083('u)001:2730: gnod byed kyis gtsor byas pa thams cad la dbul lo //
NK083('u)001:2731: de nas gnyis med spros bral gyi ngang la cham bzhag go //
NK083('u)001:2732: de bzhin du 'drer snang dang cho 'phrul la sogs
NK083('u)001:2733: pa byung ma thag /snang ba lha'i sku'i don ma
NK083('u)001:2734: rtogs par 'drer 'dzin gyi rnam rtog skyes pa'i rang
NK083('u)001:2735: gzugs yin snyam du bsam gyin lha ru yer bsam
NK083('u)001:2738: rang gzhan gnyis ka yod ma yin pa'i gnad shes par byas la /
NK083('u)001:2739: yi dam nang 'jal ba re dga' snyam du bsam gyin /
NK083('u)001:2742: tha mal gyi lus 'di tshogs su dbul lo //
NK083('u)001:2743: des na snang ba lha ru shes shing /
NK083('u)001:2744: 'dre rtog rgyun nam chad tsam na /
NK083('u)001:2748: rang la rdzogs rim gyi lta ba yod cing gnyis med kyi don go na /
NK083('u)001:2750: de yang nyam nga ba dang bag tsha ba 'drer 'dzin gyi rtog pa la sogs pa bcad cing /
NK083('u)001:2751: rdzogs rim gnyis med kyi don la bogs dbyung ba'i phyir /
NK083('u)001:2761: mdor na gnyis chos gang yang med par gnyis med kyi ngang la cham bzhag la /
NK083('u)001:2762: de'i rgyun ma yengs par sbyong ngo //
NK083('u)001:2763: de la cho 'phrul dang 'dre rtog byung na /
NK083('u)001:2764: rang gi shes pa rtse gcig tu ma song bar /
NK083('u)001:2765: 'dre rtog skyes pa'i rang gzugs shar ba yin snyam du bsams la /
NK083('u)001:2766: gnyis med rtse gcig tu hril gtong ngo //
NK083('u)001:2767: de bzhin 'drer rtog nam skyes ma thag gnyis med du yer yer bzhag go //
NK083('u)001:2769: shes pa gnyis med rtse gcig tu hril btang la /
NK083('u)001:2770: lta ba la bogs dbyung zhing gnyis med kyi don
NK083('u)001:2771: sbyangs su byung ba re dga' snyam du bsams nas
NK083('u)001:2774: stong nyid zang thal du 'gro ste /
NK083('u)001:2775: don la bden par ma grub pa'i gnad kas so //
NK083('u)001:2776: de nas rang la gnyis med kyi don skyes nas /
NK083('u)001:2778: 'drer 'dzin gyi rnam rtog rgyun nam chad tsam na /
NK083('u)001:2779: phyi rol gyi cho 'phrul rang zhir 'gro /
NK083('u)001:2780: gnyis med kyi rtogs pa nam skyes tsam na /
NK083('u)001:2781: gdon bgegs de dbang du 'du ba yin te /
NK083('u)001:2782: snang sems rten 'brel gcig yin pa'i gnad kas so //
NK083('u)001:2783: de na rang gnas tsa na bdud kyang gnas /
NK083('u)001:2784: rang zhi tsa na bdud kyang zhi //
NK083('u)001:2785: rang grol tsa na bdud kyang grol /
NK083('u)001:2786: rang 'dus tsa na bdud kyang 'dus pa yin te /
NK083('u)001:2787: des na lo gsum bsgom pa bas /
NK083('u)001:2788: gnyan sa gcig chod pa bogs che ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:2790: 'dre gdon kho na gcig pu ma yin te /
NK083('u)001:2792: mdze rims lhog pa la sogs pa nyam nga ba thams cad dam /
NK083('u)001:2793: mi gtsang mi sdug pa la sogs pa skyug bro ba thams cad dam /
NK083('u)001:2794: nyams dma' shed chung ngo tsha la sogs pa bag
NK083('u)001:2795: tsha ba thams cad dam mdor na nyon mongs rnam
NK083('u)001:2796: rtog skyes tshad la gong bzhin btang ngo //
NK083('u)001:2797: gsum pa yang dag de kho na nyid mthar phyin pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK083('u)001:2798: de ltar thun mong spyi'i spyod pas lam gyi so tshugs /
NK083('u)001:2799: brtul zhugs gsang ba'i spyod pas bogs thon te /
NK083('u)001:2802: mdor na gnyis 'dzin gyi mdud pa grol /
NK083('u)001:2806: spang sgrub dang zhen snang med de /
NK083('u)001:2807: 'khor 'das kyi dkyil 'khor 'di thams cad gnyis med
NK083('u)001:2808: ye shes kyi rba klong gcig tu cham gyis song
NK083('u)001:2809: nas / gnyis med zung 'jug bde ba chen po'i ngo bor rjen ne /
NK083('u)001:2810: de tsa na gshin rje chos kyi rgyal po lcags
NK083('u)001:2811: kyu khyer byung yang nyam nga ba dang bag tsha
NK083('u)001:2812: ba med / sangs rgyas rdo rje sems dpa' byon
NK083('u)001:2813: kyang the tshom dang sgro 'dogs bcad rgyu mi gda'
NK083('u)001:2814: ba med / 'o // de ka la yang dag de kho na nyid kyi spyod pa zhes bya'o //
NK083('u)001:2819: 'bras bu mthar 'don pa'i chos shin tu zab pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:2820: lnga pa dam tshig bstan pa ni /
NK083('u)001:2821: mnyam rjes bza' bcang bsrung ba'i dam lnga dbog /ces pas /
NK083('u)001:2826: bsrung ba'i dam tshig lnga lnga ste nyi shu rtsa lnga'o //
NK083('u)001:2830: mnyam bzhag gi dam tshig bskyed rim sgom pa /
NK083('u)001:2831: rjes thob kyi dam tshig lha dang mi 'bral zhing lus ngag tha mal du mi 'khrul ba /
NK083('u)001:2832: bza' ba'i dam tshig sha lnga bdud rtsi la rol pa /
NK083('u)001:2833: bcang ba'i dam tshig rdo rje dril bu mi 'bral ba /
NK083('u)001:2834: bsrung ba'i dam tshig snod bcud gzhal yas lha ru shes pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2836: mnyam bzhag gi dam tshig gtum mo tsan+da l+ai sgom pa /
NK083('u)001:2837: rjes thob kyi dam tshig rjes spyod thams cad gtum mo'i nyams dang mi 'bral ba /
NK083('u)001:2838: bza' ba'i dam tshig zas thams cad ye shes kyi
NK083('u)001:2839: bdud rtsi me ru byin gyis brlabs nas rol pa
NK083('u)001:2840: / bcang ba'i dam tshig rlung kha sbyor nyer gcig sgom pa /
NK083('u)001:2841: bsrung ba'i dam tshig khams mi nyams par byed pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2843: mnyam bzhag gi dam tshig dngos sam yid kyi rig ma brten pa /
NK083('u)001:2844: rjes thob kyi bde chen nyams dang mi 'bral bar byed pa /
NK083('u)001:2845: bza' ba'i zas snyoms 'jug gi tshul du rol pa /
NK083('u)001:2846: bcang ba'i byang sems lus la mi nyams par byed pa /
NK083('u)001:2847: bsrung ba'i gzungs ma mtshan ldan brten pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2849: mnyam bzhag gi dam tshig zung 'jug gnyis med sgom pa /
NK083('u)001:2850: rjes thob kyi rjes spyod thams cad de'i ngo bor 'char ba /
NK083('u)001:2851: bza' ba'i chos nyid du rol pa /
NK083('u)001:2852: bcang ba'i rtag tu gnyis med kyi don la gnas pa /
NK083('u)001:2853: bsrung ba'i gnyis med ye shes las mi 'da' 'o //
NK083('u)001:2860: rgyud thog gcig na ga nas shing 'bral med du shes pa ni man ngag gi gnad de /
NK083('u)001:2862: grol byed lam bskyed rim gyi lta ba /
NK083('u)001:2865: de las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig gi thog gcig na krong nge /
NK083('u)001:2867: grol byed lam rtsa rlung shes pa'i lta ba /
NK083('u)001:2868: gtum mo lam tsan+da l+ai sgom pa /
NK083('u)001:2870: de las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig gi thog gcig na krong nge /
NK083('u)001:2871: smin byed shes rab ye shes kyi dbang /
NK083('u)001:2872: grol byed 'og sgo bde chen gyi lta ba /
NK083('u)001:2873: thig le dbab zlog gi gnad sgom pa /
NK083('u)001:2875: de las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig dang lnga thog gcig na rug ge /
NK083('u)001:2876: smin byed bde ba chen po'i dbang /
NK083('u)001:2877: grol byed lam zung 'jug mtha' bral gyi lta ba /
NK083('u)001:2878: gnas lugs gnyis med kyi don sgom pa /
NK083('u)001:2880: de las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig dang lnga thog gcig na krong nge /
NK083('u)001:2881: de ltar shes tsa na lam la nor ba med /
NK083('u)001:2882: lam ma nor ba nas zhugs tsam na /
NK083('u)001:2883: 'bras bu phyin ci ma log pa mi thob mi srid pas shin tu zab pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:2884: de rnams gsang sngags lam gyi ngo bo yin /
NK083('u)001:2886: de dag gis lam rang gi ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2887: gsum pa lam de'i cha rkyen la gsum las /
NK083('u)001:2888: rnal 'byor lnga yi nyams len gyi gnad bstan pa /
NK083('u)001:2889: gegs sel bzhis lam gyi skyon bsal ba /
NK083('u)001:2890: bogs 'don gsum gyis lam mthar 'don pa'o //
NK083('u)001:2892: rnal 'byor lnga yis nyams su blang ba ni /
NK083('u)001:2901: rtog med chos skur nyal la 'chi rtog sbyang //
NK083('u)001:2903: gnyid log kha 'di la 'chi ba dang chos mthun pas dus gnad gal che ste /
NK083('u)001:2904: rgyun bshags dang sdom pa bzung ba la sogs pas rgyud yongs su dag par bya /
NK083('u)001:2905: nyon mongs dug gsum gyi rtog pa bcad /
NK083('u)001:2906: snga phyi'i 'brel bcad de snang dmigs kyi chos thams
NK083('u)001:2907: cad chos nyid de bzhin nyid gshis cir yang ma
NK083('u)001:2908: yin pa'i ngang la cham bzhag /gnyid rdzogs rim spros
NK083('u)001:2909: bral rtog med chos sku'i ngang du log pas 'chi
NK083('u)001:2910: ba lam du byed pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:2911: de yang snod bcud gtso 'khor thugs ka'i sa bon la bsdu /
NK083('u)001:2912: de mi dmigs pa de bzhin nyid kyi ngang la nyal bas 'chi rtog lam du bslang /
NK083('u)001:2913: gnyis pa ldang ba'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK083('u)001:2914: 'gag med longs skur langs te skye rtog sbyangs //
NK083('u)001:2916: ldang ba skye ba dang chos mthun pas tho rangs
NK083('u)001:2917: gnyid sad ma thag /rdzogs rim stong pa'i ngang nas
NK083('u)001:2918: rig pa 'gags med lha'i sku ru krong bsam /
NK083('u)001:2919: de skye ba sbyang ba yin /
NK083('u)001:2920: de nas las rgyu 'bras kyi gnad shes par bya ste /
NK083('u)001:2921: rang yi dam gang byed kyi dge sbyor gnad du btang bas bogs gzhan bas che ste /
NK083('u)001:2922: tho rangs kyi dus de na zas zos pa dwangs snyigs phyed de dwangs ma rtsa mig tu khrems /
NK083('u)001:2924: rtsa sbug thams cad stong sang nge yod pa'i dus der /
NK083('u)001:2925: phyi nang gsang gsum gyi rten 'brel gang yang skye sla ste /
NK083('u)001:2929: sems gnyis med ye shes su 'char ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:2930: sman la sogs pa'ang dro gong la btang zhing /
NK083('u)001:2931: rims srung la sogs pa'ang dro gang la byed do //
NK083('u)001:2932: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyang tho rangs
NK083('u)001:2933: kho nar sangs rgyas pa'i rgyu mtshan yang de yin
NK083('u)001:2934: no // gsum pa za ba'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK083('u)001:2935: dbang bzhi'i bdud rtsir brlab la bza' btung rol //
NK083('u)001:2937: phyi nang gi sbyin sreg don 'dra bas /
NK083('u)001:2938: dbang bzhi'i zas la zas kyi rnal 'byor bzhi yod de /
NK083('u)001:2939: bskyed rim lam du byed na /
NK083('u)001:2940: zas ye shes kyi bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs la /
NK083('u)001:2941: lto bar dkyil 'khor bskyed de lha la lha thim pa'i tshul du rol /
NK083('u)001:2942: gtum mo lam du byed na /
NK083('u)001:2943: zas ye shes kyis me ru byin gyis brlabs te /
NK083('u)001:2944: me la me bsnon pa'i tshul du rol /
NK083('u)001:2945: 'og sgo bde chen lam du byed na /
NK083('u)001:2946: zas thabs shes rab bde bar byin gyis brlabs la /
NK083('u)001:2948: bzhi pa rdzogs rim lam du byed na /
NK083('u)001:2949: zas snang stong lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes su byin gyis brlabs te /
NK083('u)001:2950: chos nyid la chos nyid rol /
NK083('u)001:2951: mdor na rang nyams su gang len pa'i ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag nas /
NK083('u)001:2952: de dang gnyis su med par longs spyod pas zas
NK083('u)001:2953: ci zos pa ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyu ru 'agro'o
NK083('u)001:2954: // bzhi pa rgyun gyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK083('u)001:2955: sna tshogs thabs kyis bzung la lam du btang //
NK083('u)001:2957: lam tshul bzhin byed pa'i rnal 'byor pa la /
NK083('u)001:2958: thams cad nas thams cad du nyon mongs pa rang rgyud pa spyad du med pas /
NK083('u)001:2959: skyes tshad thabs khyad par can gyis gnad nas bzung la /
NK083('u)001:2960: yang dag pa'i lam du btang ngo //
NK083('u)001:2961: de la nyon mongs pa ni dug lnga yin la /
NK083('u)001:2962: de lam du btang tshul ni /
NK083('u)001:2963: sems 'dod chags su lam skyes tsam na de'i ngo bo la blta zhing /
NK083('u)001:2964: ngang la bzhag pas gshis ci yang ma yin pa'i stong pa la /
NK083('u)001:2966: bde stong gnyis med kyi ngo bor mngon du gyur pa ni 'dod chags rdo rje'o //
NK083('u)001:2967: de'i ngo bo so sor rtog pa'i ye shes so //
NK083('u)001:2968: zhe sdang gi ngo bo la blta zhing rang la bzhag pas /
NK083('u)001:2971: gsal stong gnyis med kyi ngo bor mngon du gyur pa ni zhe sdang rdo rje ste /
NK083('u)001:2972: de'i ngo bo me long ye shes so //
NK083('u)001:2973: gti mug gi ngo bo blta zhing ngang la bzhag pas /
NK083('u)001:2976: mi rtog stong pa'i ye shes su gyur pa ni gti mug rdo rje'i //
NK083('u)001:2977: de'i ngo bo chos dbyings ye shes so //
NK083('u)001:2979: nga rgyal bde stong mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK083('u)001:2980: phrag dog gsal stong bya grub ye shes /
NK083('u)001:2981: yang mi dge bcu yang dug lngar 'dus /
NK083('u)001:2982: dug lnga yang dug gsum du 'dus te /
NK083('u)001:2986: de thabs kyis bzung bas nyams su myong /
NK083('u)001:2988: dug gsum rang ga ma las ldog /bslab pa gsum yin no //
NK083('u)001:2989: 'dod chags kyi ngo bo la blta zhing ngang la bzhag pas bde ba ru myong /
NK083('u)001:2991: 'dod chags rang ga ma las log pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:2992: zhe sdang gi ngo bo la bltas shing ngang la bzhag pas gsal bar myong /
NK083('u)001:2994: zhe sdang rang ga ma las ldog /ting nge 'dzin gyi bslab pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:2995: gti mug gi ngo bo la bltas shing ngang la bzhag pas /
NK083('u)001:2998: gti mug rang ga ma las ldog /shes rab kyi bslab pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:2999: nyon mongs skyes tshad la de bzhin gnas nas bzung la lam du btang ngo //
NK083('u)001:3000: lnga pa dus gnad kyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK083('u)001:3001: dro srod skyes shar 'da' kha bar do bltem //
NK083('u)001:3004: nyon mongs pa drag po dang rnam rtog rtsub mo skyes pa /
NK083('u)001:3005: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes shar ba /
NK083('u)001:3006: 'chi ba'i dus bar do rnams la gnad nas bzung ba gal che ste /
NK083('u)001:3007: de yang tho rangs snga dro'i dus na zas kyi dngas snyigs phyed /
NK083('u)001:3009: khams dang blo gsal bar yod de /
NK083('u)001:3010: skyon yon gnyis ka'i stobs che ba /
NK083('u)001:3011: gnad du btang ba gal che'o //
NK083('u)001:3012: srod la nyal ba'i dus na thig le stobs zhan /
NK083('u)001:3016: skyon yon gyi stobs che bas /
NK083('u)001:3017: thabs kyis bzung ba gal che'o //
NK083('u)001:3018: nyon mongs pa drag po dang /
NK083('u)001:3019: rnam rtog rtsub mo skyes pa'i dus su lam du ma thong na /
NK083('u)001:3020: cher srog gi bar chad 'ong zhing /
NK083('u)001:3022: ting nge 'dzin gyi gegs byas nas yang dag pa'i
NK083('u)001:3023: lam 'chol bas gnad nas bzung la lam du btang
NK083('u)001:3024: ngo // gnyis med kyi ye shes skyes nas shes
NK083('u)001:3025: pa mi rtog pa'i ngo bor hril song ba'i dus
NK083('u)001:3026: ngo // na / thabs kyis gnad nas bzung la lam du btang ngo //
NK083('u)001:3027: de gnad du song ba'i ngang la skad cig kyang ma yengs par /
NK083('u)001:3028: gdan de'i thog 'khrul 'khor de'i khongs su yun ring du bsgom pa yin /
NK083('u)001:3029: 'dun pa dang smon lam la sogs pa thams cad
NK083('u)001:3030: kyi rten 'brel de'i dus su bsgrigs pa yin no
NK083('u)001:3031: // de ni mi 'grub ka med yin la /
NK083('u)001:3032: de las gzhan pa tha mal gyi sems rnam rtog dang 'dres pas bsgrigs kyang mi 'grig ste /
NK083('u)001:3033: sgrig po rang yang rnam rtog yin pa'i phyir /
NK083('u)001:3034: grang nad la grang bas mi phan pa bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:3035: nam zhig 'chi ba'i dus su gang gis mtshams sbyar
NK083('u)001:3036: ba'i lam de nyid kyi stobs su hril 'gro bas
NK083('u)001:3037: / bzang po'i rten 'brel bsgrigs pa gal che ste /
NK083('u)001:3038: sdig pa'i las thams cad brjed du bzhug /dge ba'i las thams cad dran par byas /
NK083('u)001:3039: nyams len gang brtan pa'i steng du shes pa rtse gcig tu btang la /
NK083('u)001:3040: 'khrul snang skad cig kyang med par bya'o //
NK083('u)001:3041: mdor na dus de rnams su legs tshogs kyi rten 'brel bsgrig go //
NK083('u)001:3042: bar do'i dus gnad la gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:3043: rab bar do med par sangs rgyas pa /
NK083('u)001:3044: 'bring bar do nas sangs rgya ba /
NK083('u)001:3045: tha ma skye ba len lugs so //
NK083('u)001:3046: dang po rab la bzhi ste /
NK083('u)001:3049: mi rtog pa'i ye shes 'char tshul /
NK083('u)001:3050: de ngos zin nas sangs rgya lugs so //
NK083('u)001:3053: sa chu la thim pas lte ba'i rtsa mdud 'jig /sa rlung mal 'khyug /lus po lci /
NK083('u)001:3055: smig rgyu lta bu'i snang ba 'char /
NK083('u)001:3057: chu me la thim pas snying kha'i rtsa mdud 'jig chu rlung mal 'chug /kha sna skam /
NK083('u)001:3059: du ba lta bu'i snang ba 'char ro //
NK083('u)001:3061: me rlung la thim pas mgrin pa'i rtsa mdud 'jig /me rlung mal 'chug /drod 'thul /
NK083('u)001:3063: srin bu me khyer lta bu'i snang ba 'char /
NK083('u)001:3065: rlung rnam par shes pa la thim pas gsang gnas
NK083('u)001:3066: kyi rtsa mdud 'jig /rlung gi rlung mal 'chug /dbugs
NK083('u)001:3068: 'od kyi snang ba bag tsam 'char ro //
NK083('u)001:3069: de ltar 'byung ba thim pa dang /
NK083('u)001:3070: dbang po'i nyams yul lnga 'gag go //
NK083('u)001:3071: gnyis pa rtog pa 'gag tshul ni /
NK083('u)001:3072: rtsa dbu ma'i mar sna na /
NK083('u)001:3073: me'i dwangs ma a'i gzugs su yod pa /
NK083('u)001:3074: ro ma'i nus pa nyams nas gyen la 'gro bas dmar lam 'char /
NK083('u)001:3075: de'i tshe 'dod chags kyi rtog pa 'gags /
NK083('u)001:3077: pha'i dwangs ma ham yig gi gzugs su yod pa /
NK083('u)001:3078: rkyang ma'i nus pa nyams te thur la babs pas dkar lam 'char /
NK083('u)001:3079: de'i tshe zhe sdang gi rtog pa 'gags /
NK083('u)001:3080: de nas spyi bo khyab byed kyi rlung mal 'chug /nag lam 'char /
NK083('u)001:3081: de'i dus su gti mug gi rtog pa 'gags /
NK083('u)001:3083: nga rgyal dang phrag dog rang 'gags su 'gro ste /
NK083('u)001:3084: dug gsum po rtsa gsum du 'dus pa'i phyir ro //
NK083('u)001:3085: de'i tshe phyi dbugs chad do //
NK083('u)001:3086: gsum pa mi rtog pa'i ye shes 'char tshul ni /
NK083('u)001:3088: nang dbugs ma chad pa'i bar der /
NK083('u)001:3090: zla ba mar 'gro ba'i dus der /
NK083('u)001:3091: dbu mar rlung sems tshud de /
NK083('u)001:3092: de gsum dbu mar gnas shing rtog tshogs 'gags pa'i gnad kas /
NK083('u)001:3093: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes sangs rgyas chos
NK083('u)001:3094: sku'i dgongs pa zan gcig za yun tsam cig 'char
NK083('u)001:3095: ro // bzhi pa de ngos zin nas sangs rgya lugs ni /
NK083('u)001:3096: de ltar goms 'dris byas pa dang /
NK083('u)001:3097: gdams ngag bstan pa'i stobs kyis /
NK083('u)001:3098: rang byung lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes de rang
NK083('u)001:3099: ngo shes pas chos sku ma bu 'phrod nas sangs
NK083('u)001:3100: rgya ste / de nas rig pa tshangs bug nas 'thon te /
NK083('u)001:3101: chos kyi dbyings su gshegs pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:3102: de ni dbang po rab bar do med par sangs rgyas pa'i man ngag go //
NK083('u)001:3103: gnyis pa dbang po 'bring bar dor sangs rgyas pa'i man ngag la bzhi las /
NK083('u)001:3104: 'byung ba thim lugs dang rtog pa 'gag lugs gnyis sngar dang 'dra /
NK083('u)001:3105: gsum pa chos nyid bar do 'char tshul ni /
NK083('u)001:3106: dbang po rab kyi ltar rtog med chos sku'i dgongs pa ngos ma zin par /
NK083('u)001:3107: rig pa snying nang na gnas pa de /
NK083('u)001:3108: rtsa dar dkar gyi skud pa lta bu'i lam nas
NK083('u)001:3109: zhugs te de nas phyir 'thon pa dang bem rig
NK083('u)001:3111: brgyal ba sangs nas chos nyid kyi bar do sgra 'od zer dang thig le'i snang ba 'char ro //
NK083('u)001:3112: sgra ni chos nyid ma'i rang sgra dbyar dgun 'byed
NK083('u)001:3113: pa'i 'brug sgra lta bu che la drag pa 'char
NK083('u)001:3114: / 'od ni rig pa'i rang mdangs gsal la dwangs pa 'char /
NK083('u)001:3115: 'od kyi gseb na zer 'phro ba sos ka thang
NK083('u)001:3116: la smig rgyu lta bu mer mer ba 'char ro
NK083('u)001:3117: // bzhi pa rang ngo shes nas sangs rgya lugs ni /
NK083('u)001:3118: da lta ngo sprad pa dang nyams su blang ba'i dbang gis /
NK083('u)001:3119: sgra 'od zer gyi snang ba de dag rang byung
NK083('u)001:3120: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes su shes nas sangs
NK083('u)001:3121: rgya'o // de yang yang goms 'dris kyi bye brag gis /
NK083('u)001:3122: rdzogs rim stong nyid kyi don la goms pa'i rnal 'byor pa yin na /
NK083('u)001:3123: sgra 'od zer gyi snang ba de dag snang stong
NK083('u)001:3124: gnyis med kyi ye shes su shar nas chos kyi
NK083('u)001:3126: bskyed rim lha'i rnal 'byor la goms pa yin na /
NK083('u)001:3127: sgra 'od zer gyi snang ba de dag rang mdangs
NK083('u)001:3128: lha'i dkyil 'khor du shar nas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK083('u)001:3130: rdzun snang stong pa'i rnal 'byor pa yin na /
NK083('u)001:3131: sgra 'od zer gyi snang ba de dag rmi lam
NK083('u)001:3132: sgyu ma lta bur shar nas sprul pa'i sku ru
NK083('u)001:3133: sangs rgya'o // 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang snang du shes pa'i rnal 'byor pa yin na /
NK083('u)001:3134: sgra 'od zer gyi snang ba de dag rang shar
NK083('u)001:3135: dang rang grol du shes nas ngo bo nyid kyi
NK083('u)001:3136: sku ru sangs rgya ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:3137: des na rang re nyams len bzhi po gang la gnas bltas la /
NK083('u)001:3138: gang la nyams rtogs skyes pa'i sgo nas bar do bcad do //
NK083('u)001:3139: gsum pa dbang po tha ma skye ba len lugs ni lnga las /
NK083('u)001:3142: gsum pa yid kyi lus grub tshul ni /
NK083('u)001:3143: rten 'brel brgyad kyis yid lus grub ste /
NK083('u)001:3144: 'od rang snang ma shes pa ni ma rig pa /
NK083('u)001:3145: de'i dbang gis rlung lngar 'dus nas 'khor bar byed pa 'du byed /
NK083('u)001:3146: de las shes pa gsal du song nas yul 'dzin skye ba ni rnam shes /
NK083('u)001:3147: de las bar do'i yid dang yid kyi lus gnyis 'byung /
NK083('u)001:3148: de las shes pa rno myur du skye bas skye mched 'byung /
NK083('u)001:3149: de yul dang 'phrad par reg pa /
NK083('u)001:3150: des bde sdug myong ba tshor ba /
NK083('u)001:3151: de la chags sdang skyes pa sred pa /
NK083('u)001:3152: de ltar brgyad kyis yid lus grub bo //
NK083('u)001:3153: bzhi pa bar do'i snang ba 'char lugs ni /
NK083('u)001:3154: sngar gyi bag chags dang las kyi snang ba 'char te /
NK083('u)001:3155: sngar gyi yul dang khyim du 'ong //
NK083('u)001:3156: nye drung kun dang yid kyis 'grogs //
NK083('u)001:3157: zas dang gnas dang brten sa'i nges pa med /
NK083('u)001:3158: yid kyi lus kyis dri ma'i zas za /
NK083('u)001:3159: skye gnas dang ma'i mngal dang /
NK083('u)001:3160: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku dang /
NK083('u)001:3161: rdo rje gdan ma yin pa thams cad la thogs pa med par 'gro /
NK083('u)001:3166: kha char bu yug gi snang ba 'char ro //
NK083('u)001:3168: skye mched gsal zhing yid kyi dbang po tshang ba /
NK083('u)001:3169: lha'i mig rnam par dag pa dang /
NK083('u)001:3170: bar do'i sems can nang gis mthong ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:3171: lnga pa skye ba phyi ma len tshul ni /
NK083('u)001:3172: gong gi rang mdangs mchog gi 'od gsal de nub nas /
NK083('u)001:3173: thun mong 'od kyi lam lnga shad kyis 'char ro //
NK083('u)001:3174: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa de rang ngo ma shes la /
NK083('u)001:3175: kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pas gzhan du brtags /
NK083('u)001:3176: gzhan snang la 'dzin pa zhugs pas 'gro drug tu skye ba yin te /
NK083('u)001:3177: ri dwags rgya ru tshud pa'am /
NK083('u)001:3178: sbrang ma bal rgyar 'thums pa bzhin no //
NK083('u)001:3179: de yang 'od dkar po la 'dzin pa zhugs na dmyal ba /
NK083('u)001:3181: nag po la dud 'gro ser po la mi /
NK083('u)001:3182: ljang gu la lha dang lha ma yin tu skye'o //
NK083('u)001:3183: de'i dus su rigs drug gi sdug bsngal bsam la /
NK083('u)001:3184: 'od lnga po gang la'ang 'dzin pa mi bya /
NK083('u)001:3185: bar do'i shes pa 'di bsgyur sla bas /
NK083('u)001:3186: dran pas zin na bde ba can lta bur 'dun pa btang bas the tshom med par skye'o //
NK083('u)001:3187: lam de'i gegs bzhi'i skyon bsal bstan pa ni /
NK083('u)001:3189: gnyis pa lam gyi gegs bsam pa la bzhi ste /
NK083('u)001:3190: ting nge 'dzin nyams kyi gegs bsal ba dang /
NK083('u)001:3191: lus na tsha sdug bsngal gyi gegs bsal ba /
NK083('u)001:3192: sems rnam rtog lha 'dre'i gegs bsal ba /
NK083('u)001:3193: rkyen snang glo bur grib kyi gegs bsal ba'o //
NK083('u)001:3196: bying rgod nyams gsum bcos la lam du btang //
NK083('u)001:3201: phan pa'i nyams lam du btang ba /
NK083('u)001:3202: gnod pa'i nyams grogs su 'khyer ba /
NK083('u)001:3203: phan gnod med pa'i nyags bogs su 'don pa'o //
NK083('u)001:3207: 'thibs pa la sogs pa ni don mthun te bying ba'o //
NK083('u)001:3208: de la bying ba ni rig pa'i rang mdangs ma rnyed pa /
NK083('u)001:3209: rmugs pa ni gsal ba'i nyams kyis ma zin pa /
NK083('u)001:3215: g.yo sbun la sogs pa don mthun te rgod pa'o //
NK083('u)001:3216: de la g.yo ba ni sems gnas su mi 'dod pa /
NK083('u)001:3217: sbun pa ni yud tsam gnas kyang yun ring du mi gnas pa /
NK083('u)001:3218: 'phro ba ni shes pa yul la 'jug pa'o //
NK083('u)001:3220: 'og 'gyus ni sems gnas snyam byed pa la ma tshor bar 'gyus pa'o //
NK083('u)001:3221: rang 'gyus ni sems gnas gyin 'dug gsal gyin 'dug
NK083('u)001:3222: snyam pa'i tshor ba phra mo gcig sgom gyi gseb
NK083('u)001:3223: tu zhugs pa'o // rgod pa la gnyis /
NK083('u)001:3224: gzhan rgod ni shes pa rkyen gsum gyis rgod pa /
NK083('u)001:3225: rang rgod ni gnas cha med pa shes pa yeng ba'o //
NK083('u)001:3226: mdor na bying rgod gnyis ka'i rkyen gyi rtsa ba gcig ste /
NK083('u)001:3227: shes pa gzhur la ma thebs par btang snyoms su lus pa las byung ngo //
NK083('u)001:3229: bying na snying khar sems bzung la shes pa zhur gzhur chun gcun /
NK083('u)001:3230: rtse gcig mdung tshugs chig dril du bsgom mo //
NK083('u)001:3231: des bying mi nus te srang du chud 'agro'o //
NK083('u)001:3232: rgod na sems lte 'og tu bzung la zhur gzhur /
NK083('u)001:3233: chun gcun la phur tshugs su bsgom /
NK083('u)001:3234: des chig dmigs la hril song nas 'phro rgod mi yong ngo //
NK083('u)001:3235: mdor na rtse gcig phur tshugs su song na bying rgod gnyis ka mi yong ngo //
NK083('u)001:3236: gsum pa phan pa'i nyams lam du btang ba ni /
NK083('u)001:3237: bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin bzang po'am /
NK083('u)001:3238: byams snying rje zhen log gi blo'am /
NK083('u)001:3239: mos gus la sogs pa gting nas lhongs pa skyes
NK083('u)001:3240: pa'i dus su de'i ro myangs nas lus ngag gi
NK083('u)001:3242: nyams de nyid rlung kha log nas yal 'gro bas /
NK083('u)001:3243: bdag gzhan dbang du 'gro ba'i bya ba bskyed la /
NK083('u)001:3244: de nyid rlung sems kyi rten 'brel nyams su shes
NK083('u)001:3245: pa'i blo gros kyis dgar 'dzin dang zhen snang med
NK083('u)001:3246: par / rang gi ngo bo la bltas shing ngang
NK083('u)001:3247: la bzhag pas gnyis med ye shes kyi ngo bor
NK083('u)001:3248: par / 'char te / nyams zhen med kyi sna mi bskyil bar 'ur brkyang ngo //
NK083('u)001:3251: snying rje btsan thabs su skyes nas ngu ba la sogs pa byung na /
NK083('u)001:3253: lta ba'i gnad shes par bya ste /
NK083('u)001:3254: de'i ro mi myong bar ngang la bzhag go //
NK083('u)001:3255: ro myang na rgyal po la sogs pa'i tshe 'phrul yin pa'ang srid do //
NK083('u)001:3256: bzhi pa gnod pa'i nyams grogs su khyer ba ni /
NK083('u)001:3258: snying rlung khams 'dus la sogs pa ci byung yang nyams snang du shes par byas te /
NK083('u)001:3259: zhum zhing byur du mi blta /
NK083('u)001:3260: snang yul dang 'dzin sems rang shar rang grol bas /
NK083('u)001:3262: yon tan du mi bzung bar rang shar rang grol byung rgyal du bskyang ngo //
NK083('u)001:3263: lnga pa phan gnod med pa'i nyams bogs su 'dod pa ni /
NK083('u)001:3264: kun gzhi la 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad lhun gyis grub cing /
NK083('u)001:3265: sa bon gyi tshul du gnas /
NK083('u)001:3266: rdo rje'i lus la rtsa yig rlung sems su gnas
NK083('u)001:3267: pa de dag ngo sprad cing ting nge 'dzin gnad
NK083('u)001:3271: rlung sems dwangs bag chags 'dag cing yon tan gyi sna slong bas /
NK083('u)001:3272: 'khor 'das kyi snang ba sna tshogs nyams la 'char ro //
NK083('u)001:3273: de dag la bu ga yod na rlung 'jug /rtog pa skyes na bdud ldang /
NK083('u)001:3274: btang snyoms su lus na lam du mi 'gro bas /
NK083('u)001:3275: thams cad nyams su shes par bya ste /
NK083('u)001:3276: gang la yang skyon du mi blta /
NK083('u)001:3279: nyams snang rang shar rang grol du bskyangs bas thams cad bogs su thon nas 'gro ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:3280: mdor na sgrub pa byed pa'i dus na /
NK083('u)001:3281: res blo las su rung zhing dge sbyor 'phel te /
NK083('u)001:3282: sgom chen rgyang glu tsam re /
NK083('u)001:3283: res blo bkol du mi gtub dge sbyor 'grib /
NK083('u)001:3285: sgom chen yus kha stong nge /
NK083('u)001:3286: mdor na mtho dman gyi nyams sna tshogs skye bas /
NK083('u)001:3287: zhums pa dang khengs pa med par /
NK083('u)001:3288: zhen med byung rgyal du gnad nas bzung zhing lam du btang /
NK083('u)001:3289: sgrub pa la thang lhod ltem kyang med par byas pas /
NK083('u)001:3290: thams cad bogs su thon 'gro ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:3291: gnyis pa lus la na tsha duhkha'i gegs bsal ba ni /
NK083('u)001:3292: nad kyi gzhi rgyu rkyen 'bras ngos bzung bcos /
NK083('u)001:3301: kun gzhi dang rtsa khams bag la nyal bag chags kyi tshul du gnas so //
NK083('u)001:3304: ma rig pa dang bdag tu 'dzin pa ste /
NK083('u)001:3308: nyon mongs rnam rtog 'dre dang bcas pa'o //
NK083('u)001:3311: tsha grang bad kan gzer thabs sbos nad kyis gtsos byas te nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'o //
NK083('u)001:3312: de la lhan cig skyes pa'i nad rgyu gtso /
NK083('u)001:3313: kun brtags kyi nad rkyen gtso /
NK083('u)001:3314: nad gang la yang 'di lnga tshang dgos te /
NK083('u)001:3318: mtshams sbyor rnam rtog /mjug sdud rlung /
NK083('u)001:3320: de yang rgyu 'dod chags kyi sa bon kun gzhi la yod /
NK083('u)001:3321: rkyen 'dod chags drag pos bslangs bas grang ba'i nad du ldang /
NK083('u)001:3322: na'o thu'o snyam pa'i rnam rtog gis mtshams sbyar /
NK083('u)001:3323: des thur sel gyi rlung log /gdon mo rigs blta'o //
NK083('u)001:3324: de bzhin du rgyu zhe sdang gi sa bon /
NK083('u)001:3325: rkyen zhe sdang drag pos bslangs /
NK083('u)001:3326: rnam rtog gi sa mtshams sbyar /
NK083('u)001:3327: mnyam gnas kyi rlung khog /nad mkhris pa /
NK083('u)001:3329: rgyu gti mug gi sa bon /
NK083('u)001:3330: rkyen nyon mongs pa gti mug /na'o thu'o snyam pa'i rnam rtog gis mtshams sbyar /
NK083('u)001:3331: gyen rgyu'i rlung log /gdon klu gnod /
NK083('u)001:3333: rgyu phrag dog gi sa bon /
NK083('u)001:3334: rkyen phrag dog drag pos bslangs /
NK083('u)001:3338: rgyu nga rgyal gyi sa bon /
NK083('u)001:3339: rkyen nga rgyal drag pos bslangs /
NK083('u)001:3341: khyab byed kyi rlung log /gdon rgyal po gnod /
NK083('u)001:3344: rgyu ma rig pa yin pas lhan skyes kyi ye shes ngos bzung /
NK083('u)001:3345: rkyen nyon mongs pa yin pas sems mnyam par bzhag
NK083('u)001:3346: /mtshams sbyor rnam rtog yin pas rnam rtog rgyun bcad
NK083('u)001:3347: / mjug sdud rlung yin pas rlung gnad du btang /
NK083('u)001:3348: rgyab brten lha 'dre yin pas lha 'dre'i rnam rtog spong ngo //
NK083('u)001:3349: de ltar byas pas nad gang yang dag go //
NK083('u)001:3350: dang po bcos pa la gsum ste /
NK083('u)001:3353: tha ma dmigs pas bcos pa'o //
NK083('u)001:3356: spros bral ngang bzhag rgyun chad skyes dang sel //
NK083('u)001:3358: nad de la phan pa'i sman thun gcig mi btang /
NK083('u)001:3359: rim gro ye ge brgya pa gcig kyang mi bya /
NK083('u)001:3362: bzo med byung rgyal du bskyang /
NK083('u)001:3363: spros bral rang lugs rtog med kyi ngang la cham bzhag /de ltar bzhag pas rnam rtog rgyun chad /
NK083('u)001:3364: rtog med ye shes skyes nas nad de nyid sel lo //
NK083('u)001:3365: de la sngon 'gro'i dus su nad mi btsal /
NK083('u)001:3366: dngos gzhi'i dus su nad mi bsgom /
NK083('u)001:3367: rjes kyi dus su nad kyi ro mi myong ngo //
NK083('u)001:3372: gnod pa'i zas za 'phrig bcad ltos med bskyur //
NK083('u)001:3380: nad de 'dod thog tu khyer la /
NK083('u)001:3381: nad khyod la brten nas rnam rtog gi gras thag
NK083('u)001:3382: bcad du yod pa re dga' snyam du bsam ste
NK083('u)001:3383: / shes pa dga' seng nge btang /
NK083('u)001:3384: nad de la gnod pa'i zas bza' /
NK083('u)001:3386: de la dri chen bar pa blangs la drod ma yal ba tshugs tshad du bza' /
NK083('u)001:3387: dri chu bar pa yang tshugs tshad btung ngo //
NK083('u)001:3388: de nas rlung rtsol bsgoms pas /
NK083('u)001:3389: stod nad yin na skyugs su 'gro /
NK083('u)001:3390: smad nad yin na bshal du 'gro /
NK083('u)001:3391: nad 'thon pa dang gcod sman du 'gro /
NK083('u)001:3399: thu ru yong bas mi yong ngam snyam pa'i rtog
NK083('u)001:3400: pa med par 'khu 'phrigs rbad bcad la ltos med
NK083('u)001:3402: gsum pa ro snyoms pa ni /
NK083('u)001:3403: 'phrang byung tsa na lung blang dgos pas shes pa grub bton te dge sbyor gsal btab la /
NK083('u)001:3405: rim gro dang sman dpyad mi bya /
NK083('u)001:3406: na zugs de nyid kyi ngo bo la bltas shing ngang la bzhag pas /
NK083('u)001:3407: nyams myong skyes pa yin na rang yal du 'gro /
NK083('u)001:3408: rtogs pa skyes pa yin na gsal stong du 'char /
NK083('u)001:3409: tha ma yang nad la duhkha dang rnam rtog mi 'byung ngo //
NK083('u)001:3410: gsum pa dmigs pas bcos pa ni /
NK083('u)001:3411: dkar dmar nag po'i h'u 'phros steng 'og 'don /
NK083('u)001:3415: rang yi dam gyi lha ru bsgom /
NK083('u)001:3416: de'i snying gi dkyil du h'u mthing nag nas tsam zhig bsgom /
NK083('u)001:3417: de nas nad gang yin brtags la /
NK083('u)001:3418: tsha ba yin na snying nang gi h'u las h'u dkar po nas tsam zhig 'phros pas /
NK083('u)001:3419: khog stod thams cad bskor nas /
NK083('u)001:3420: nad thams cad khab len gyis lcags bsdus pa ltar 'ub ril bsdus /
NK083('u)001:3421: spyi gtsug nas 'thon te nam mkha' la yal bar bsam la rlung gyen la 'bud /
NK083('u)001:3422: grang ba yin na snying gi h'u las h'u dmar po nas tsam zhig chad nas /
NK083('u)001:3425: 'og sgo nas 'thon te sa'i gting du song bar bsam /
NK083('u)001:3426: yan lag gi nad dam brang ngar la sogs pa khol bur nan /
NK083('u)001:3427: gang na sar h'u nag po nas tsam gcig bsam ste thams cad bsdus nas /
NK083('u)001:3428: skrangs ba'i dmigs sam sor mo'i rtse nas 'thon par bsam mo //
NK083('u)001:3429: ngos ma zin pa'i nad la /
NK083('u)001:3430: snying nang gi h'u las h'u mthing ga chad de lus kyi stod smad thams cad bskor /
NK083('u)001:3431: nad kun bsdus nas rlung gang rgyu ba'i sna nas 'thon te bar snang la yal bar bsam mo //
NK083('u)001:3432: ngang la bzhag pa la shes pa mi rtog pa'i ngang du hril 'gro dgos /
NK083('u)001:3433: bzlog bsgom la the tshom dang 'khu 'phrigs med par ltos med du rkyang bskyur dgos /
NK083('u)001:3434: dmigs pa la shes pa chig dmigs su 'gro dgos /
NK083('u)001:3435: de gsum ka la blo khel zhing 'gyur drag pa gal che'o //
NK083('u)001:3436: gsum pa sems rnam rtog lha 'dre'i gegs pas bsal ba ni /
NK083('u)001:3437: rang las gzhan med yang 'khu 'phrigs bcad /
NK083('u)001:3439: nyams thal thol skyes pa'i dus su rtsa gnas kyi rten 'brel dang /
NK083('u)001:3440: rnam rtog gi ther zug gis bdud rigs lha 'dre'i cho 'phrul dang thar thug 'ong ngo //
NK083('u)001:3441: de la 'jigs pa dang nyam nga'i rnam rtog skyes
NK083('u)001:3442: na myur du gnad nas bzung la lam du btang
NK083('u)001:3443: ngo // de rang gar bzhag pa'am /
NK083('u)001:3445: phyis sgrub pa nam byed kyi bar chad du yong ba yin no //
NK083('u)001:3446: gzhan yang mtho dman gyi gegs byung ba de nyid lam du ma thongs na /
NK083('u)001:3447: byis sgrub pa byed pa'i dus na /
NK083('u)001:3448: de nyid skyed dang bcas pa cig byung nas bar chad du 'gro ba yin pas /
NK083('u)001:3449: lam du btang ba gal che ste /
NK083('u)001:3450: spyir lam du btang ba ni /
NK083('u)001:3451: rtsa ba rang gi rnam rtog lam srang bcad la /
NK083('u)001:3452: gdon dang cho 'phrul ltar snang ba 'di rang gi blo 'khrul ba'i rang ngor shar ba yin te /
NK083('u)001:3453: rang las gzhan pa'i lha 'dre ni gtan nas rang med do //
NK083('u)001:3454: de yang gdon dang cho 'phrul ltar snang ba'i dus nyid na /
NK083('u)001:3455: blo 'khrul pa'i rang ngor shar ba yin te /
NK083('u)001:3456: de nyid skye 'gag gnas gsum dang bral zhing ma grub par shes pa'i gnad kyis /
NK083('u)001:3457: cho 'phrul nam byung ba'i dus na /
NK083('u)001:3461: rnam rtog gsal stong du shar tsam na lam du bslangs pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:3466: snying stobs gding dang ldan par byas te /
NK083('u)001:3467: nyam nga dang bag tsha 'khu 'phrigs rbad bcad la /
NK083('u)001:3468: bdud tshogs 'dre dmag gang byung yang /
NK083('u)001:3469: ba spu'i bu ga gcig kyang skyod par mi nus /
NK083('u)001:3470: bar chad bya ba rang mi 'ong /
NK083('u)001:3471: tshugs rang mi tshugs bsam pa'i sems dpa' bar bya'o //
NK083('u)001:3472: 'dre dang bar chad na ba la sogs pa byung na ni snyam pa'i rnam rtog mang ba ni /
NK083('u)001:3473: 'dre la sna len byed pa yin no //
NK083('u)001:3474: des na lha 'dre ltar snang ba thams cad rang
NK083('u)001:3475: gi rnam rtog gi rang gzugs shar ba yin gyi
NK083('u)001:3476: / gzhan du grub pa spu tsam yang med pas /
NK083('u)001:3481: gnad nas bzung la lam du btang ngo //
NK083('u)001:3482: bzhi pa glo bur grib kyi gegs bsal ba ni /
NK083('u)001:3483: dam nyams grogs gnas zas kyi grib bzhi bsal //
NK083('u)001:3493: sel zhugs pa las byung ngo //
NK083('u)001:3498: mi sdig po che dang glo bur du 'phrad pa'am /
NK083('u)001:3505: 'dre can la sogs pa las 'ong ngo //
NK083('u)001:3511: dam khang la sogs par bsdad pa las grib 'byung ngo //
NK083('u)001:3516: sdig zas la sogs pa las grib 'byung ngo //
NK083('u)001:3517: de rnams kyis lus la nad 'jug /ting nge 'dzin 'grib /
NK083('u)001:3519: de dag gi rmi rtags ni /
NK083('u)001:3520: dam tshig nyams na nam srod la /
NK083('u)001:3523: grogs la grogs kyi mi gtsang ba rang la gos pa 'byung /
NK083('u)001:3524: gnas la gnas mi gtsang bar 'dug pa 'byung ngo //
NK083('u)001:3525: zas la rang gi mi gtsang ba dang /
NK083('u)001:3526: dri mas gos pa'i zas zos pa'i 'byung ngo //
NK083('u)001:3527: de dag bsal ba la rab 'bring tha gsum las /
NK083('u)001:3537: grib skong la sogs pa mang du bya'o //
NK083('u)001:3538: lam de'i bogs 'don gnad du btang ba ni //
NK083('u)001:3540: gsum pa lam de'i bogs 'don la gsum ste /

NK083('u)001:3593: dran pa bsten cing zhi gnas kyis bogs 'don no //

NK083('u)001:3596: bogs thams cad kyi gnad do //

NK083('u)001:3602: nyon mongs gnad nas bzung la lam du btang //

NK083('u)001:3606: skyes pa de nyid gnad nas bzung zhing lam du btang la bogs 'don dgos so //
NK083('u)001:3610: ji ltar btang ba'i thabs so //

NK083('u)001:3625: 'phrul 'khor de'i khongs su lam du btang dgos so //

NK083('u)001:3640: no // ye shes kyi gzhi la de med na lam du mi 'gro ba yin no //

NK083('u)001:3692: rtog pa gzhan gyis bar ma chod par lam du btang ngo //

NK083('u)001:3701: de la ngan rtog ma zhugs /
NK083('u)001:3706: rtog pa gzhan gyis bar ma chod par lam du btang /

NK083('u)001:3710: de dag lam gyi cha rkyen no //

NK083('u)001:3717: gdul bya thugs rjes gzigs tshul la gzhan gyis log rtog bzlog pa'o //

NK083('u)001:3722: lam sgrib byed kyi dri ma dag pa'i tshe /

NK083('u)001:3808: thun mong gi mtshan dang dpe byad do //

NK083('u)001:3872: bu sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa mkhyen pa

NK083('u)001:3876: gcig dang tha dad las grol bar bzhugs so //

NK083('u)001:3878: par las 'bras chos nyer lngar snang bas gcig dang
NK083('u)001:3879: bral la / 'bras chos nyer lnga yang kun tu

NK083('u)001:3885: bral lo // dgongs pa gcig tu bden na /
